longDescription: Brush smart, get rewarded. The quip Smart Electric Toothbrush Starter Kit earns you amazing rewards (like free brush heads, products, gift cards, and more) as you track and coach better oral health habits with the free quip app. It has a Bluetooth® Smart Motor, premium All-Color design, and the same timed sonic vibrations as our original ADA-Accepted brush. quip's simple and sustainable brush also includes a premium handle you keep for life, a replaceable soft-bristle brush head (tongue scraper on back), a replaceable AAA battery, and a multi-use travel cover that doubles as a stand and mirror mount. Connect one or more Bluetooth® Smart Brushes to the quip app (iOS & Android), then automatically track your brushing routine offline: duration, coverage, strokes and intensity. To help improve your oral health habits, tap the app for tailored tips, coaching, and more. You can also earn rewards you'll love just for brushing two minutes, twice a day. Unlike some electric brushes that are big and bulky, quip is slim and lightweight with a long-lasting 3-month battery (no wires or bulky charger). Simply click the "q" button to power a gentle, effective clean with all the guiding features dentists recommend: sensitive sonic vibrations, 2-minute timer, 30 second pulses. The sleek, travel-ready design easily packs into any pocket, purse, or bag for on the go. Plus, it's water-resistant and shower-safe.  Like most quip oral care products, the quip Smart Electric Toothbrush is American Dental Association-Accepted, and shown to help remove plaque, and help prevent and reduce gingivitis. On a refill plan, quip automatically delivers a fresh Brush Head Refill every 3 months for $5 with free shipping and a lifetime warranty. Subscribe to get your first refill free, and see why quip has over 20,000 5-star reviews. Better oral health, made simple, affordable, and enjoyable.

longDescription: Everything You Need to Pursue Your Wellness Goals! Get the emotional and physical benefits of exercise without changing your daily routine with Cubii JR2+! Use our newest model to help you burn calories, targeting the lower body and obliques, and increase leg strength, mobility, and your daily activity level. The built-in display screen tracks your strides, distance, speed, active time, and calories burned, while seamlessly syncing with the Cubii mobile app and other fitness tracking apps. Getting Active Just Got Easier with JR2+. Cubii JR2+ is our second seated elliptical that connects to the Cubii mobile app via Bluetooth, allowing you to sync your progress across our app, Apple Watch, Fitbit, and HealthKit. Begin pedaling toward your health and fitness goals and join the thousands of striders who are building strength, burning calories, and reaching their health and wellness goals in the Cubii Communitii™! More Compact, JR2+ Fits Seamlessly into Your Life. The Cubii JR2+ compact design fits seamlessly into your life! This model weighs less than 20 pounds and includes a built-in handle making this model easier to carry from room to room. Our included Attachable Wheel Cup helps hold the front wheel of any office chair in the correct position while you pedal or can be removed when not needed. Get Connected! Unlock Your Potential with JR2+ and Cubii Studio+. Cubii Studio+ is our online exercise class library that allows you to access 300+ on-demand workout classes whenever you want! Cubii Studio+ lets you personalize your workout routine and fits the needs of wellness seekers of all ages, abilities, and lifestyles. Join our community by registering for free today to access the platform online or in the Cubii mobile app.
name: Cubii - JR2+ Seated Elliptical with Bluetooth Connectivity, Low Impact Exercise for Home or the Office - Aqua

longDescription: ENRICH PRO (BEHIND THE EAR) HEARING ENHANCEMENT PRODUCT OFFERS THE HIGHEST QUALITY FEATURES AVAILABLE IN A CONVENIENT READY-TO-WEAR HEARING PRODUCT.  The Premier utilizes the newest Powered by Lucid patented technology to deliver a more natural sound quality that is superior to traditional “compression” hearing products, providing the wearer better communication in noisy environments as well as enhanced comfort in quiet situations. The result is clear hearing and comfort.  Low-level noise suppression provides for improved comfort in quiet environments. Noises such as air conditioning, refrigerator motors or internal microphone noise are all reduced by this system. This helps keep quiet situations quiet.  Our Dynamic Feedback Canceller employs a patented technique that adapts continuously to changing circumstances while maintaining excellent sound quality. Unwanted feedback is suppressed and stopped without sacrificing sound quality or gain.  Two listening modes to adjust the device to accommodate Conversation and Crowd environments.  Nano Technology coats every aspect of the hearing product at a nanoscopic level and protects much more thoroughly than alternative approaches. The result is a truly durable and invisible liquid repellent coating (inside and out). Our revolutionary Nano-coating does not affect working components, maintaining the look, feel, and functionality of the device.  Lucid Hearing Enrich Pro BTE employs the latest software to provide greater processing power and increased battery life. Low battery indicating signal alerts user to change batteries prior to complete battery drain.  Includes comfort dome fitting tips to cover a wide range of ear canal sizes. longDescription: At Lucid Hearing, our Mission is Helping People Hear Better. We amplify the outside world for clearer conversations and more enjoyable experiences.  Lucid Hearing ENRICH Personal Sound Amplifier (PSAP) incorporates technology developed from years of expertise. Don’t miss a sound or a secret. Enhance your hearing and enjoy conversations, concerts, television, music and more. Listening Modes: Program one is for use in everyday situations from enhancing a speaker’s voice when you are seated in the last row of a church or auditorium to enhancing the sounds of nature during a leisurely stroll through the outdoors. Program two is adjusted to further enhance the high frequency sounds of nature. Distant birds will sound like they are sitting on your shoulder and you will be the first to hear their faint sounds.  Program three is tuned to provide a full spectrum of sound, allowing you to fully experience the richness of music or low rumble of a race track while still protecting your hearing. Unlike sound plugs that distort sound, program three provides a natural full sound experience. longDescription: The Lexie Lumen OTC Hearing Aid includes all the hearing aid features you need at a price you can afford. Take control of your hearing with the award-winning Lexie app. Simply connect your hearing aids via Bluetooth to your smartphone and unlock the ability to change volume and environmental settings to suit your hearing needs. Take a hearing check when your hearing aids arrive and your hearing aids will be programmed according to your hearing ability. Easily select the hearing environment from six settings and adjust your devices to your environment. These environments include Everyday Use, Noisy Indoor, Music, Outdoor, Telecoil, and Companion Mic* (*requires a Lexie Companion Mic). You also have access to Lexie Experts through the app, 6 days a week, for free. Don’t settle for anything less than a dual-microphone hearing aid. Lexie’s dual-microphone improves the quality of speech understanding in noisy environments and customizes settings to individual needs. The Directional Hearing microphones amplify the sounds you want to hear and cancel out the sounds you don’t want to hear. Adaptive Noise Reduction allows you to determine if sounds are more speech-like or more noise-like. These features allow you to have the best sound experience. longDescription: Body Cardio is the first smart scale to provide a cardiovascular check-up in less than 30 seconds from the comfort of your home. longDescription: Experience personal training in your living room with the ProForm Carbon E7 front-drive SMART Elliptical. With an included 30-day iFIT membership, you can stream immersive on-demand video workouts directly through your elliptical’s beautiful 7” HD touchscreen display. Transform your living room into a boutique studio class, blasting calories alongside virtual classmates or follow your favorite iFIT trainers on a journey around the world in captivating destination workout series across all 7 continents. iFIT technology allows your trainer to automatically adjust your elliptical’s resistance and incline for a fully immersive workout optimized to your current fitness level and goals. Your elliptical’s 7” smart HD touchscreen tracks your workout stats across time and iFIT-compatible equipment, so the elevation you climb on your elliptical and the miles you run on your treadmill are both accounted for. In manual workout mode, cycle through 24 levels of progressive resistance or adjust your elliptical into a 20-degree incline to engage in anaerobic exercise that targets specific muscle groups and accelerates weight loss.

[{'feature': 'Virtually Invisible
Eargo hearing aids fit discreetly inside your ear canal where no one can see them. Eargo Neo will not interfere with glasses, face coverings, and hats like traditional behind-the-ear hearing aids.'}, {'feature': 'Rechargeable
Eargo has eliminated the need for replacing tiny batteries by making all our hearing aids rechargeable. An overnight charge delivers up to 16 hours of use. Our latest-generation digital processor features an extended bandwidth for improved speech clarity, smart feedback cancellation, and advanced noise reduction that improves listening comfort in noise over previous Eargo hearing aids.'}, {'feature': 'Natural sound with "open fit" design
Eargo’s patented Flexi TetraPalms not only suspend the hearing aids inside your ear canal, but also provide an “open” fit so you do not feel “plugged up” as you would with traditional hearing aids, resulting in a more natural sound experience.'}, {'feature': 'Warranty
Neo HiFi comes standard with a 2-year repair warranty and 1-year loss/damage protection. This is our longest warranty when compared to other Eargo hearing aids.'}, {'feature': "Personalize Your Hearing

Eargo is renowned for its world-class hearing telecare support. Eargo hearing aids come with lifetime support from our team of licensed hearing professionals, who have decades of experience helping people start their hearing journey and getting the most out of your Eargos.'}]
longDescription: Legal Disclaimer: By ordering this item, I am certifying that: I am at least 18 years old. I have had the opportunity to visit Eargo's website to review their User Instructional Brochure, support tab with various informational videos, and know that I can call a live Eargo Customer Service Representative for assistance. I have been advised by Eargo Hearing Inc. that the Food and Drug Administration has determined that my best health interest would be served if I had a medical evaluation by a licensed physician (preferably a physician who specializes in diseases of the ear) before purchasing a hearing aid. I do not wish to obtain a medical evaluation before purchasing a hearing aid. This is Eargo Neo HiFi. If you’re not hearing life to the fullest, you’re not living life to the fullest. It’s time to take control of your hearing loss and do it on your terms with Eargo Neo HiFi - a virtually invisible hearing loss solution designed for people with mild to severe high-frequency hearing loss. Fitting discreetly (almost invisibly) inside your ear canal, Eargo Neo HiFi is packed with great audio fidelity, background noise reduction, and feedback control. Plus, Eargos are easily rechargeable (no batteries required), simple to use, and come with lifetime telecare support from our team of licensed hearing professionals. If that’s not enough, you can use ithe Eargo Neo HiFi  mobile app to conveniently adjust, program, and personalize your hearing experience for each ear...like adjusting your HiFi stereo.
name: Eargo Neo HiFi Hearing Aid - Black

longDescription: The RW500 Rower is a new approach to an old-school workout. An efficient form of exercise, the rower’s core strength is focusing on yours. Quickly and smoothly adjust your resistance using the SMR Silent Magnetic Resistance. Manually change the adjustable air resistance to fine-tune your resistance or to switch the amount of cooling air you feel during your strength-building workout. You can also adjust the pedals to find the most comfortable position or to target specific muscle groups. After you finish your workout, fold up the rower using the SpaceSaver design and roll it away with the built-in transport wheels for convenient storage. Complete with an adjustable console that allows you to track your stats, including strokes, time, watts, and estimated calories burned, the RW500 is the perfect rower for you.

longDescription: Dive into dynamic, high-energy workouts with the world’s best personal trainers on the ProForm Pro 5000 smart treadmill. With an included 30-day iFIT membership, you can transform your treadmill into your own home fitness hub. Stream thousands of live and on-demand workouts led by expert iFIT Trainers who teach you proper form and motivate you to succeed. Virtually travel the world with Global Workouts, running from the beautiful beaches of Bora Bora to the jagged peaks of Machu Pichu. Choose from live and on-demand Studio Classes, where you can sweat alongside virtual classmates and compete against other iFIT members on the Leaderboard. Thanks to Automatic Trainer Control, your treadmill’s speed and incline will auto-adjust to match global terrains and meet trainer suggestions. If you have a Bluetooth heart rate monitor (sold separately) you can experience ActivePulse, exclusive technology that adjusts your workout intensity to keep you in your target heart rate zone. Stream all your favorite workouts through a luxurious 14” HD touchscreen, and run with confidence knowing your treadmill is powered by a self-cooling Mach Z motor. You’ve got this!

longDescription: Get a complete fitness experience with interactive personal trainers in your living room. The ProForm Carbon CX home Exercise Bike comes with a 30-day iFIT membership (sold separately), bringing the power of personalized training into the comfort of your living room. Embark on a virtual trip around the world, cycling from the breathtaking red rock deserts of Southern Utah to colorful Chilean streets. Transform your living room into a boutique studio class with on-demand video workouts led by charismatic coaches that automatically adjust your bike’s resistance to meet your workout’s requirements or mimic real-world terrain. An LCD window display with an incorporated device shelf provides a secure platform for your tablet or smartphone, and a SMART Bluetooth connection allows your iFIT Trainers to communicate with your exercise bike to automatically adjust your resistance. A set of 3 Lb. dumbbells give you the ability to engage in full-body cross-training to develop comprehensive health, while 16 digital resistance levels give you total control of your workout while on your bike. Finally, an inertia-enhanced flywheel fortified with SMR Silent Magnetic Resistance delivers a smooth, quiet workout with every use - so you can train without waking the kids or bothering the neighbors.

shortDescription: Exercise Bike

longDescription: If you’re looking for a comprehensive training tool, look no further than the ProForm Pro 2000 smart treadmill. With an included 30-day iFIT membership, you can transform your treadmill into your own home fitness hub. Stream thousands of live and on-demand workouts led by expert iFIT Trainers who teach you proper form and motivate you to succeed. Virtually travel the world with Global Workouts, experiencing everything from vast African savannahs to frozen arctic peaks. Stream live and on-demand Studio Classes, where you can sweat alongside virtual classmates and compete against other iFIT members on the Leaderboard. With Automatic Trainer Control, your treadmill’s speed and incline will auto-adjust to match global terrains and meet trainer suggestions. If you have a Bluetooth heart rate monitor (sold separately) you can experience ActivePulse, exclusive technology that adjusts your workout intensity to keep you in your target heart rate zone. Stream all your favorite workouts through a luxurious 10” HD touchscreen, and run with confidence knowing your treadmill is powered by a self-cooling Mach Z motor. You’ve got this!
name: ProForm - Pro 2000 - Black
shortDescription: Treadmill

longDescription: The best way to improve at your sport is with a little help. Develop your pitching skills with help from the Cimarron Sports 4- by 6-Foot Baseball/Softball Backstop. This batting cage backstop can be used for pitching practice and as a net saver. This training aid is a vinyl backstop with a rectangular strike zone target. This vinyl baseball and softball backstop is designed to help pitchers practice their throwing techniques for better aim and precision. While the batting cage backstop gives pitchers something to aim at, it also protects your netting. This allows pitchers to throw at full-strength without worrying about damaging the batting cage netting. This baseball backstop is constructed of heavy-duty vinyl-coated nylon canvas. The material stops the hardest pitched balls, no problem. Overall, the pitcher backstop measures 6 feet high by 4 feet wide and easily attaches to your existing batting cage net.
name: Cimarron Sports - Baseball Softball Batting Cage Net Target Vinyl Backstop Only - Black
shortDescription: The best way to improve at your sport is with a little help. Develop your pitching skills with help from the Cimarron Sports 4- by 6-Foot Baseball/Softball Backstop. longDescription: IQbuds 2 MAX are multi award-winning hearing buds that personalize and enhance your listening experience. Named as Time Magazine Best 100 Inventions of 2020, IQbuds 2 MAX set a new standard in augmented hearing devices combining all the benefits of a high-end earbuds with advanced features that allow you to control your world of sound. Best in class active noise cancelling technology allows you to turn down your world while you enjoy pitch perfect sound fidelity. With Ear ID™ you can personalize your listening experience based on your own hearing profile. World sound control features include Speech-in-Noise Control (SINC) that enables you to boost conversations, FOCUS that allows you to focus on sounds in front of you, and World EQ which filters the level of bass and treble in your sound environment. IQbuds2™ MAX enables hands free phone calls and the ability to connect to SIRI and Google Assistant. With the compact charging case you can enjoy 20 hours of on-the-go Bluetooth streaming and 36 hours of hearing enhancement. Connect IQbuds2™ MAX to IQstream™ TV (sold separately) to personalize your TV volume while allowing others in the room to listen at their comfortable levels. IQbuds2™ MAX are the perfect device for when you feel like you need some situational hearing enhancement but you’re not quite ready for a hearing aid. Required to be worn in both ears simultaneously for optimal listening and performance. Hearing profile customization requires user to complete the EAR ID profile in the IQbuds App for iOS or Android.
name: Nuheara - IQbuds 2 MAX Personal Hearing Amplifier - Black

longDescription: Discover the advantage of close cutting performance. The REMINGTON® SmartEdge™ Advanced Foil Shaver features a revolutionary cutting system that delivers our most efficient shave*. The ActiveHybrid Cutting System combines the advantages of rotary and foil shaving, with an inner hybrid cutter to pre-trim longer hairs and outer foils to capture even the shortest hairs. The AccuCut Blades feature an open arched design, reducing noise and vibration for a more comfortable shaving experience*. You can find your ultimate comfort with the WETech™ 100% waterproof design, allowing you to shave dry, with foam, and even in the shower. The rechargeable lithium battery delivers up to 60 minutes of cordless runtime, with a 5-minute quick charge to deliver enough power for a last-minute shave. Plus, the included stubble attachment makes it simple to create a clean, relaxed stubble to enhance your look. *compare to Remington F5800

shortDescription: HyperSeries SmartEdge™ Advanced Foil Shaver

[{'feature': 'Virtually Invisible

Eargo is renowned for its world-class hearing telecare support. Eargo hearing aids come with lifetime support from our team of licensed hearing professionals, who have decades of experience helping people start their hearing journey and getting the most out of your Eargos.'}, {'feature': 'Worry-Free Contactless Charging
For Eargo 5, we swapped contact pins for magnets to keep your Eargos securely in place for easier, contactless charging and 16 hours of usage when fully charged.'}]
longDescription: Eargo 5 started a revolution for Eargo. We set out to design a new hearing aid that delivers premium sound quality in our smallest size ever while also allowing it to be customized to a person's unique hearing preferences, and we delivered. Our clients responded enthusiastically! With our best sound quality yet, and noise reduction to make even the most challenging listening environments more comfortable, you can use Eargo 5 and hear with confidence. The power to improve your hearing is in your hands, delivered directly to you and expertly supported by Eargo's licensed hearing professionals. With Eargo 5 we introduced the SoundMatch feature in our mobile app. In about 10 minutes you can easily screen your hearing through Eargo 5 hearing aids and customize the performance to your unique hearing levels, including adjusting the noise reduction. All of this completed on your time without visiting hearing offices. Control your sound with just a tap. You can also choose one of four presets on the hearing aids. Or use the Eargo 5 mobile app to tailor the sound to your hearing preferences. And if you need personalized support by one of our licensed hearing professionals, we're here for you. Simply call Eargo, start a conversation through the Eargo app or schedule an appointment on your smart phone. It’s the best Eargo sound experience to date. Legal Disclaimer: By ordering this item, I am certifying that: I am at least 18 years old. I have had the opportunity to visit Einargo's website to review their User Instructional Brochure, support tab with various informational videos, and know that I can call a live Eargo Customer Service Representative for assistance. I have been advised by Eargo Hearing Inc. that the Food and Drug Administration has determined that my best health interest would be served if I had a medical evaluation by a licensed physician (preferably a physician who specializes in diseases of the ear) before purchasing a hearing aid. I do not wish to obtain a medical evaluation before purchasing a hearing aid.
name: Eargo 5 Hearing Aid - Black

Our diverse roster of instructors lead you through a wide range of classes and musical genres (from amped up EDM to pull-on-the-heartstrings country and everything in between) for an incredible experience that's personalized for everyone. With specifically designed immersive features like Hi-Fi speakers positioned towards the rider, every ride on the SoulCycle at-home bike is heart-pounding—and most of all, fun. The commercial-grade steel frame accomodates all shapes and sizes, and invites you to confidently (and safely) move through exciting, engaging choreography that will leave you feeling like a superstar—physically and mentally. longDescription: Get ultra fast results for your body grooming routine with the Remington ShortCut Pro Body Groomer with Handle. The stainless steel blade is 60% wider to trim more body hair with each pass, and it's dual-sided so you can trim in either direction. It's finally easy to trim your back hair! Just clip the trimmer onto the extendable handle and use the different length settings to reach all areas of your back. Mesure up to 400 lb./182 kg in 0.1 lb or 50 g increments.  The scale has a surdy 11.8 in. x 11.8 in. glass platform (300 mm x 300 mm) and a height of only 0.9 in. (23.5 mm), making it easy to store.'}, {'feature': 'High-Visibility Readout

Scale operates on 3 AAA batteries (included).'}, {'feature': 'Limited 10-Year Warranty
Designed for optimal reliability and durability, this scale is built to last and covered under warranty for a full 10 years.'}, {'feature': 'To Note:
The weight-only mode will give accurate body weight readings for all users.  The body analysis mode will give accurate readings for most people, but it is not calibrated for body analysis measurements of the following groups:  Anyone under the age of 18 or pregnant women.'}]
longDescription: Track your progress with every weigh-in on the WW Body Analysis Scale by Conair. This Bluetooth-enabled scale stores data for up to 9 users, weighs up to 400 lb. (182 kg), and syncs detailed body measurements directly to the free WW Scales by Conair app on your smart device. It can pair with Apple Health, Google Fit, or other health and wellness apps that maximize your motivation. An easy-to-read dashboard shows your progress as it’s updated in the app. Step onto the wide, comfortable platform and watch the scale reveal your body fat, body water, muscle mass, bone mass and BMI measurements on an easy-to-read LCD screen. WW members can weigh in at home and sync results to the official WW app. Set your goals and see results with the scale that keeps you connected to success! This innovative scale performs weight-only readings as well as an advanced Bio-Impedance Analysis (BIA)—a comprehensive method for assessing body fat, body water, bone mass, and muscle mass. BIA measurements, along with the built-in Body Mass Index (BMI) indicator, determine total body composition, including hydration levels and body fat versus lean body mass, so you can track your personal health and weight trends in greater detail. The digital scale memorizes up to 9 personal profiles, making tracking effortless with easy syncing from scale to smart device via Bluetooth®. Simply download the free WW scale app on your iPhone or Android to track and chart your results, earn badges for consistency, and progress toward your goal! (Don’t do digital? No worries. A smart device isn’t required for using the scale.) Durably built, with a sleek, modern styling, the WW Body Analysis Scale by Conair is an advanced tool for measuring and tracking wellness, so you stay motivated and ready to meet your goals!
name: Conair - W/W Bluetooth Body Analysis Scale - Black

longDescription: The HidrateSpark PRO Smart Water Bottle is the world's smartest water bottle! Stainless Steel vacuum-insulated body keeps drinks cold for up to 24 hours, prevents sweating and allows for a pure water taste. Both variations of lids feature a protective spout cover. The Chug lid includes a button lock to prevent accidental spills. This 100% BPA-free bottle includes an easily accessible rechargeable battery on the bottom of the bottle with a fast charging cable so your bottle can always stay charged while you're on-the-go. This new design also includes an improved sensor technology with clinically proven accuracy within 3% of manual readings through Mayo Clinic trials. Using a built-in sensor, the HidrateSpark PRO bottle tracks your water intake and syncs via Bluetooth to the brand’s FREE hydration app on your phone (available on iOS and Android). When a user falls behind on their hydration goal, LED lights embedded in the sensor puck glow in customizable patterns as a reminder to stay on track. Users also receive reminder notifications throughout the day via the hydration app. Perfect as a gift for friends and family—track each other's progress and make staying hydrated a fun activity!
name: Hidrate - HidrateSpark PRO 21 oz. Chug - Black

Each comes  with  a  spout  cover  to  keep  out  dirt  and  germs  and  an  integrated  carry handle that makes it easy to take on-the-go.

It provides people who need occasional hearing help with an affordable do-it-yourself solution like reading glasses. It is perfect for providing a needed boost to hear speech clearly.  Enlite has been meticulously engineered to produce the highest fidelity possible. The frequency response of Enlite has been shaped specifically to improve speech intelligibility. When playing or listening to music, Enlite can process peak inputs up to 115 dB without distortion. It also has a 16 kHz bandwidth, at least double the bandwidth of other OTC hearing aids on the market.  Enlite has just one dual-mode switch for the user to adjust. Both versions of Enlite will run up to 12 days on a single battery, and there is an audible indicator to let you know when the battery is running down. Everything needed to get started comes in the box, including multiple eartips for a comfortable fit, batteries, and a leather carrying case.
name: Lucid Hearing - OTC Enlite Deluxe Hearing Aids - BLACK

longDescription: The TV HearGear high resolution listening system with Awareness mode is an all-in-one solution for enhancing your TV watching experience.  Whether you want the best sound experience while watching a movie or the ability to watch TV in bed while your partner sleeps beside you, TV HearGear has you covered. Using a state-of-the-art Bluetooth transmitter and earphones you get a latency free, high-definition experience utilizing Qualcomm AptxHD technology for a sound better than any other similarly priced products in the market today. longDescription: At Felix Gray, we know that electronic devices are a necessary, and sometimes inevitable, part of our lives. That’s why, at Felix Gray, we offer the hardest-working Blue Light filtering glasses for the hardest-working individuals. We create effective, research-backed products to improve our relationship with technology because we truly care about our Digital Wellness. Felix Gray filters 15x more of the most impactful Blue Light than any other clear lenses. In doing so, we hope to empower us all to thrive in our modern world. Felix Gray’s Nash is a beautiful fit for your face, with elegant square frames and a signature keyhole bridge. The Nash features a slightly narrower bridge to provide a sense of steadiness and comfort. Whether you’re staring at a computer screen for extended periods of time or catching up with late-night reading on your tablet, Felix Gray’s Blue Light filtering glasses are just what you need to relieve symptoms of Digital Eye Strain and support your total well-being. Designed with the modern world in mind, these are our original, proprietary, and virtually clear Blue Light Glasses perfect for everyday wear.

longDescription: If you sometimes struggle to understand speech, or enjoy soft music, the BeHear ACCESS smart assistive listening Bluetooth headset may be just what you need. The personalizable BeHear ACCESS hearing amplifier can help you participate in face-to-face communication in challenging environments, appreciate the full spectrum of live music, watch TV at volume levels that don’t annoy others, conduct efficient mobile phone calls, comprehend your favorite podcast, and enjoy the music you love. BeHear ACCESS uses advanced technology developed in Israel and field-proven worldwide to reduce background noise, clarify speech, and deliver superb sound quality. BeHear ACCESS maps your unique hearing profile and then provides the precise amount of sound amplification needed to ensure your listening experience is both positive and comfortable.  BeHear ACCESS is not: a hearing aid or medical device addressing high levels of hearing loss. Note: If you suffer from severe or profound hearing loss we encourage you to consult with us before purchase.
name: BeHear ACCESS - Personalized Hearing Amplifier - Black

features:
[{'feature': 'Comfortable, ears free listening
BeHear PROXY wireless Bluetooth speaker rests gently on your shoulders, bringing TV sound closer to your ears and eliminating room reverberation.'}, {'feature': 'Optimal for TV watching
Low latency aptX technology achieves perfect audio-video synchronization. The sound source is brought to the stereo speakers just inches from your ears, allowing you to reduce the TV volume significantly.'}, {'feature': 'Loud and clear mobile and video calls

Using the extractable earbuds, conduct a private mobile call or listen to the television without disturbing others.'}, {'feature': 'Use with or without hearing aids
If you have hearing aids, use BeHear PROXY to bring the sound close to your ears and reduce volume at the source. Or alleviate hearing aid fatigue by using the neck speaker without your aids!'}, {'feature': 'Extensive battery life
The rechargeable battery provides up to 45 hours of charge for calls using the retractable earphones, up to 40 hours for media play using the earphones, or up to 10 hours of media play using the loudspeakers.'}]
longDescription: This Bluetooth® stereo neck speaker delivers a rich and comfortable listening experience for television watching, gaming, music streaming, and hands-free mobile and video calls. BeHear PROXY rests lightly on your shoulders to bring the sound source within inches of your ears, keeping them free (which makes BeHear PROXY ideal for use with hearing aids). You’ll be able to enjoy clear dialogue and superior stereo audio at low volume levels, preserving harmony in your home! Extractable earphones provide privacy, when desired, or confine the audio to your ears in consideration of others. BeHear PROXY can also be used as a loudspeaker when multiple people want to enjoy the same program or participate in the same conference call. When bundled with our HearLink® PLUS Bluetooth audio transmitter, BeHear PROXY provides unmatched accessibility and improved language comprehension. This bundle will allow you and others to enjoy watching programs together, as the audio will be transmitted via the television speakers and BeHear PROXY simultaneously.
name: BeHear PROXY - Wireless Neck Speaker for TV, Music & Phone Calls - Black

longDescription: Get back in the game more quickly without the worry of stiff muscles. The Sharper Image Powerboost Massager is the post-workout recovery tool you need and the muscle repairer you deserve. This state-of-the-art massage gun uses percussion to target sore muscles and tight knots, helping you unwind after a long workout. Change the strength of the percussion to suit your body's needs and help break up lactic acid before your next workout. The nodes loosen tight or stiff muscles to reduce soreness and get you back in the game quicker. And it's whisper quiet with low vibration on the ergonomic handle, so it's the most comfortable massage gun you'll find anywhere. Take it with you to the gym, on vacation, or to your next game.
name: Sharper Image Powerboost Deep Tissue Massager - Black

[{'feature': 'Barber-quality beard styling
Easily maintain even long beards at home with ease; neatly trim, shape, and detail with smooth barber-style results without having to visit the barber'}, {'feature': 'Advanced blade design trims thick beards effortlessly
Capture more whiskers in one pass; ER-GB96-K the with a wider space between the blades to efficiently gather, capture and cut even dense, tangled, and unruly beard hair.'}, {'feature': 'Powerful, comfortable trimming
High-performance, high-torque motor powers through dense facial hair, eliminating snags and pulls for clean, smooth cutting'}, {'feature': 'Choose your length
The quick-adjust beard trimmer dial works with attachments to provide 58 trim length settings from 1-30mm; trim as close as 0.5mm with no attachment'}, {'feature': '4 comb attachments
Slide-on comb attachments neatly align hair for even trimming in different lengths; use the detail attachment for precise trimming and stray hairs'}, {'feature': 'Ergonomic grip for comfortable trimming
Help keep your hand and arm from fatigue and discomfort when trimming; slim, ergonomic trimmer design provides a solid grip for maximum comfort and total control'}, {'feature': 'Easy to clean
IPX7 waterproof body rinses clean under water; blade snaps on and off gently and easily for thorough cleaning with included brush'}, {'feature': 'Use cordless or corded
Use cordless for up to 50 minutes, or plug in and used corded for longer use. The rechargeable Ni-MH battery fully charges in an hour'}, {'feature': 'Don’t forget replacement blades for your best trim
Replace blade every 3 years or when dull. for close, comfortable trimming every day; ER-GB96-K pairs with replacement blade WER9620Y (sold separately)'}]
longDescription: Long beard, medium, or short, Panasonic GB96-K Mens Beard Trimmer makes it easy for everyone from beginners to the more experienced to achieve barber-quality hair, beard and mustache trimmer styling at home. An acute-edge, ultra-sharp stainless-steel blade uses wider-tipped and spaced blades to catch more hair in one stroke for more efficient trimming. And, the electric beard trimmer is powered by a High-Torque motor, calibrated for clean, comfortable trimming of even dense beards, with no snagging or pulling. Four included comb attachments work the quick-adjust dial to provide up to 58 trim length settings from 0.5MM (with no attachment) to 30MM, to create the style and length you want while the 5mm-wide detail attachment provides precise trimming and control. The Panasonic GB96-k beard clipper has an IPX7 rating and waterproof design so you can trim in the shower or dry anytime. A single 1-hour charge provides up to 50 minutes of cordless use, or plug in and use corded for longer use. Unplug unit from electrical outlet when washing or using for wet trimming. To maintain peak performance, rinse blades under water after each use and replace blade every 3 years or when dull with replacement blade WER9620Y.
name: Panasonic - ER-GB96-K Rechargeable Beard Trimmer with 4 Attachments Wet/Dry - Black

[{'feature': 'A safe, powerful trimmer for everyone

Skin Protective Blade Technology helps reduce skin irritation on thin, delicate skin, and glides around every curve while trimming; round-edge blades help minimize skin irritation and trim as close as 0.1mm, for a smooth, shave-like experience'}, {'feature': 'Skin guard attachment for precise trimming
Skin guard safely trims sensitive areas like armpits, bikini area and groin, letting you trim as close as 2mm'}, {'feature': 'Trim longer hair with adjustable comb attachment
Uniformly trim thicker body hair; adjustable comb with built-in dial lets you adjust trimming length from 3 to 12 mm, to uniformly trim hair on chest, legs, arms and more'}, {'feature': 'Trim hard-to-reach areas with ease
Ergonomic, I-Shaped body design for total control, and unique V-shaped head to trim in narrow and complicated places such as the back, groin, and buttocks'}, {'feature': 'Designed for all-over grooming
Trimmer design makes body grooming simple, from back & legs to a full Brazilian. V-shaped head is nimble in narrow places and body is easy to control and cuts in both directions, allowing you to trim more quickly and tailor cutting to match your needs'}, {'feature': 'Smoother shaving with power motor
Powerful trimmer motor can cut 5,300 hairs per second, gliding through even thick hair with ease. Motor ensures hair is cut quickly and cleanly, without tugging or pulling'}, {'feature': 'Wet/Dry groomer charges fast & travels easily
Comfortably groom in or out of the shower; quick full charge in just 1 hour enables 50 minutes of use; hard travel case included for easy packability'}, {'feature': 'Keep trimmer working great
Ensure you rinse excess hair from trimmer after every use, and frequently oil blade to ensure peak performance.  For a consistently smooth trim, replace blade when dull (about once every 3 years depending on usage) with the Panasonic WER9500P'}]
longDescription: The GK80 is a gentle, powerful two-blade electric body groomer that is built for sensitive skin all over the body, especially in the hard-to-reach areas. No need to struggle with trimming the delicate skin on the back, armpits, buttocks, bikini area or groin: this sleek, essential body hair trimmer for men and women uses Skin Protective Blade Technology to help reduce skin irritation with round-edge blade tips. The GK80 includes a skin guard attachment to trim in more sensitive areas such as groin and bikini areas, while an adjustable comb attachment (3-12mm dial) lets you uniformly trim body hair on the chest, legs and more. Driven by a motor that cuts 5,300 hairs/ sec, it needs only light pressure to glide over the skin, letting you enjoy smoother cutting with less tugging, even of hard, coarse body hair. An easy-to-hold and easy-to-use grooming tool, the Panasonic body trimmer has a unique V-shaped that lets you easily maneuver in even in narrow and complicated places--holding the end of the handle helps with hard-to-reach areas such as the back and buttocks. This wet / dry groomer can be used in or out of the shower, with or without shaving cream or foam, for maximum convenience and versatility. It charges quickly, achieving a quick full charge in just 1 hour to enable 50 minutes of use. Add replacement blade WER9500P to ensure continued peak performance. Travel pouch included.
name: Panasonic - ER-GK80-S Rechargeable Cordless Body Hair Trimmer for Unisex with 2 Combo Attachments Wet/Dry - Black
shortDescription: The GK80 is built especially for delicate skin and hard-to-reach areas: back, armpits, buttocks, bikini area, groin. Skin Protective Blade Technology helps reduce skin irritation with round-edge blade tips; a skin guard attachment sensitive groin and bikini areas, and adjustable comb attachment trim body hair on the chest, legs, and more.

[{'feature': 'RecoveryAir JetBoots Sizing Guide
Size small for heights ranging 5' - 5'5". Size medium for heights ranging 5'6" - 6". Size large for heights ranging 6' - 6'6".'}, {'feature': 'Wireless Compression Boots

RecoveryAir’s exclusive TruGrade Technology helps apply precise pressure through a true negative gradient air flow, starting from your feet moving toward your heart, to temporarily increase circulation to the treated area.'}, {'feature': 'Faster Cycles. Faster Recovery.
Complete one full cycle of boot inflation and deflation in just 60 seconds via our FastFlush Technology. This is 2-3x faster than competitors.'}, {'feature': 'Custom Control Application

longDescription: Therabody is revolutionizing pneumatic compression with the all-new RecoveryAir product line, the future of pressure massage. RecoveryAir JetBoots make recovery more convenient than ever without the need for cords. It eliminates the external pump and tubes, replacing them with integrated motors that are packed into a sleek, compact design for easy storage and on-the-go recovery. One-touch controls on the boots make for fast and easy use. With FastFlush Technology, RecoveryAir JetBoots reach the optimal point for a full and rapid pressure release in just 60 seconds–making it 2-3x faster than competitors for rapid recovery. Ultra-portable, convenient and fast.
name: Therabody - RecoveryAir JetBoots Medium - Black

The Hisho uses advanced long rail SL-Track massage technology that delivers a superior lower back, glute, and sciatic focused massage while sill delivering the deep tissue relief you need throughout the rest of the back, including your neck and shoulders. This is done by gently curving the frame in at meticulously calculated angles near the neck and lumbar region while extending the frame underneath the seat to reach the glutes.  This ensures you receive the largest coverage area of massage possible while also maintaining the highest quality of massage.  The Hisho’s full body compression system makes sure that no part of your body is missed, it’s unique high-rise calf airbags even provide massage coverage in the knees.  The Hisho’s advanced massage technology and zero gravity therapy will leave you relaxed and feeling like you’re sitting on a cloud, try yours today.

The Jin 2.0 will utilize 3 unique widths while massaging you to accommodate narrow or broad shoulder widths while delivering full body massage with its total body compression therapy system.  Your arms will be perfectly held in place using its C+U shaped compression system, preventing your arms from slipping out like other massage chairs, while massaging your arms and stimulating blood flow.  The extra-large foot and calf massage system (with foot roller) will expertly and gently massage your foot and calf (of any size legs, slim to large) with ease, and if you’re taller the 6-in extendable leg-rest will glide out to provide extra legroom.  The Jin 2 fits into your home with its zero-wall system, requiring only 2in of clearance behind the chair, and its Bluetooth speakers let you take your massage experience to the next level by enjoying your favorite music. longDescription: The Kurodo by Synca Wellness is a true executive level commercial massage chair. The precision of the Hitachi made massage robot, the quality of the Japanese massage technique, and the therapeutic deep tissue massage surpasses all other commercial massage chairs on the market. The exposed breathable fabrics have been removed wherever possible in order to provide cleanable more hygienic surfaces.  The simple and easy to use controller makes use as easy as hitting the power button but leaving just enough user controls for a discerning person to optimize the massage for their own needs.  The Kurodo by Synca Wellness is an executive level commercial grade massage chair, if you are looking for a chair for your home look at the Synca Wellness JP1100.  The Kurodo by Synca Wellness is designed for usage in a premium commercial setting such as a commercial fitness facility (gym), vertical luxury housing (condo/apartment), office, business, call center, or employee breakroom.    If you were thinking your facility should have a massage chair, look no further, you’ve found the best.

longDescription: At Felix Gray, we know that electronic devices are a necessary, and sometimes inevitable, part of our lives. That’s why, at Felix Gray, we offer the hardest-working Blue Light filtering glasses for the hardest-working individuals. We create effective, research-backed products to improve our relationship with technology because we truly care about our Digital Wellness. Felix Gray filters 15x more of the most impactful Blue Light than any other clear lenses. In doing so, we hope to empower us all to thrive in our modern world. Felix Gray's Jemison +1.0 Strength Blue Light Reader has a classic square frame. The shape makes it ideal for larger faces or for someone looking for a pair of glasses that are slightly oversized. Whether you’re staring at a computer screen for extended periods of time or catching up with late-night reading on your tablet, Felix Gray’s Blue Light filtering reader glasses are just what you need to relieve symptoms of Digital Eye Strain and support your total well-being. Designed with the modern world in mind, these are our original, proprietary, and virtually clear Blue Light Glasses perfect for everyday wear.
name: Felix Gray - Jemison +1.0 Strength Blue Light Reader Glasses (with case & cloth) - Black

longDescription: The Relieve 3D Massage Chair is a premium massage chair that offers maximum therapeutic benefit. It is filled with innovative technology and tailored to your body’s needs. This advanced massage chair features a state-of-the art, three-dimensional massage mechanism with 5 levels of deep tissue massage. Moving side to side, up and down and in and out, the mechanism mimics the hands of a professional masseuse. The L-shaped track system reaches from the neck and shoulders to the gluteus muscles. Start with the custom body scanning technology to read the body contours and adjusts the massage to fit you. Choose the auto program that fits your mood — Relieve, Extend, Stretch, Rise and Shine and Athlete are just a few of the programs available for energizing and relaxing. Choose a quick stress-relieving program or a head-to-toe complete whole-body massage in just minutes. Airbag compression therapy for the legs, arms, shoulder and feet help to reduce muscle pain and improve circulation. Calf kneading, shiatsu reflexology foot rollers and the automatic footrest extension are a must. The innovative arm massage pockets pop-up for use, then tuck away. Recline into full zero gravity with a single touch. The Relieve 3D Massage Chair is a total massage experience, like no other.

The massaging robot travels in an L-shaped track with 4 massaging nodes working from the top of your back, down your spine and all the way to your glutes, for a more complete, full body massage. The kneading, tapping, kneading with tapping, shiatsu and knocking techniques give you the feel of human hand. Use the lumbar heat feature to loosen up tight muscles and enjoy reflexology via shiatsu foot rollers to soothe aching feet. features:
[{'feature': 'Glides
Effortless glide: Quartz ceramic-coated plates glide and preheat hair to form lasting smooth curls.'}, {'feature': 'Curls
Lasting loose curls: Unique cool air system allows cool air to flow outside of barrel to immediately set your curl and protect your hair.'}, {'feature': 'Heat
High heat: Plates heat up to 400°F.'}, {'feature': 'Heat up time

No stress: Automatic safety shutoff lets you focus on styling without fear of forgetting to turn the styler off.'}, {'feature': 'Styler
Cool Air Styler'}]
longDescription: Want a quick, easy way to create gorgeous, salon-worthy curls that last? Designed with a unique cool air system, the InfinitiPRO by Conair Cool Air Styler flows cool air up through the channels in the barrel to set and protect your style for long-lasting results. Quartz ceramic-coated plates provide effortless glide to form silky, smooth curls. Cool air flows outside the barrel, quickly setting your curl while protecting against damage. You get fast, consistent heat up to 400°F for even, flawless results as the cool air locks in your look. Three heat settings, plus a cool air setting, make it easy to customize styling for your hair type. A must-have for anyone who wants to get maximum curls with minimum fuss, the InfinitiPRO by Conair Cool Air Styler features innovative technology that's simple to use. As you wrap, hair and curls take shape—the cool air coming up through the barrel ensures they set perfectly and stay that way. The cool air system does the work for you, setting cascades of curls that keep you looking like you just stepped out of the salon. Pro tip: For maximum staying power, place a section of hair between the plates, rotate the styler 180° back, wrap hair once around the outside of the barrel and glide down through the length of the hair. Set and protect your curls like a pro–quickly and easily–with this innovative styling essential from InfinitiPRO by Conair.
name: Conair - InfinitiPRO Cool Air Styler - Black

longDescription: Experience the world's closest electric shave and uncompromised skin comfort with Philips Norelco S9000 Prestige with wireless Qi-charging. Our excellent skin comfort system enables you to effortlessly get a highly efficient shave, even on a longer (up to 7-day) beard. Its new wider, rounder openings catch more hair per pass, resulting in a difference you can feel. The Smart Hair Sensor checks hair density 500 times per second and automatically adapts the shaver to your hair. Choose between 3 modes to customize your shave: 1) Comfort - for a gentle, thorough shave. 2) Dynamic - for a thorough, everyday shave. 3) Efficiency - for a quick shave that saves you time. Get a convenient dry shave or a more refreshing wet shave with gel or foam - even in the shower. Finish your look with the skin-friendly click-on precision trimmer. It is ideal for maintaining your mustache and trimming your sideburns. The premium pouch protects the shaver as well as its accessories and wireless Qi charging pad. Its thoughtful design matches the timeless elegance of the shaver. Shave longer with every charge, thanks to a powerful and long-lasting Lithium-ion battery. You'll have up to 60 minutes of shaving time – that's about 21 shaves. Wirelessly charge your shaver or any other Qi-compliant device by simply placing it on the Qi charging pad. Clean the shaver easily and thoroughly under the tap. Simply open the shaving head and rinse both sides under running water to get it perfectly clean. This shaver only operates in cordless mode. For best shaving performance, replace your shaving heads every 12 months. Use SH91/52 replacement heads, sold separately.
name: Philips Norelco 9000 Prestige Shaver with Qi Charging Pad SP9872/86 - Black

longDescription: The ES-LS9A Arc6 mens razor delivers an ultra-premium shave with six blades—two finish blades, two lift blades, and two new thick stubble blades coated with titanium—forged from the same highest-grade stainless steel used for Japanese sword making, informed by centuries of Japanese craftsmanship. Its refined texture, beautiful matte black color, and sculptured, ergonomic shape make the ES-LS9A feel substantial yet lightweight; every inner blade is inspected and marked with the date of production and lot number before shipping. Premium Cleaning and Charging Station included.

longDescription: The Worlds Thinnest Reading Glasses- At ThinOptics, our concept is simple enough -- since your smartphone is always with you, we set out to develop thin, comfortable reading glasses that fit on the back of your phone. These Readers are thin, lightweight and available in a variety of lens strengths (+1.5, +2.0, and +2.5).  Every pair of ThinOptics Readers is made of shatterproof, thermo-injection molded, optical-grade polycarbonate. The bridge is made from a shape-memory metal called Nitinol, which is 10x more elastic than spring steel and encased in medical-grade silicone tubing. They fit snugly into this elegant matte black Universal Pod Case, which can attach (via an included non-residue adhesive strip) to nearly any hard and flat surface, including the back of your smart phone or your laptop. You can also just as easily slip them into your wallet, purse or pocket -- ensuring that clear vision is Always With You!
name: ThinOptics Universal Pod with Readers 2.0 Black - Black

longDescription: The Kyota Kaizen M680 3D/4D is the complete package — designed to target your entire body for a full-body massage experience. Its 4D 6-node back mechanism is unrivaled for providing a broad back massage. Kneading massage on your back, arms, calves and feet for unmatched coverage to feel great every day! The Kaizen's 6-node back mechanism is designed to provide more contact as it travels from your neck to your glutes. Add in the tri-zone heat located in the back, arms, and feet and to help loosen up sore muscles. The exclusive advanced kneading arm mechanism combined with compression airbags can help reduce pain and inflammation in the arms, wrists and hands. Then, work your way down to your calves with the Complete Calf Kneading + Oscillation mechanism paired with the fully enclosed, wrap-round airbag compression to soothe your tired aching feet. The quick access control panels allow you to easily adjust your recline all the way to zero gravity mode. If you are worried about space, this chair is equipped with zero wall fit space-saving technology and requires just 2" of wall clearance. The Kyota Kaizen M680 3D/4D massage chair can help you change your health and your life by integrating massage therapy into your everyday wellness routine.

longDescription: Our ProtectMe Car Decals display critical information including medical conditions, syndromes and allergies for First Aid responders and Emergency Services. All ProtectMe products are designed to promote situational awareness and reassurance during an emergency.

longDescription: Train with everything you need on the NordicTrack Elite 800 Treadmill. The 3.0 CHP motor is ready to power through your toughest workouts.  Connect your tablet to your machine via Bluetooth® and use your included 30-Day iFIT Family Membership to experience thousands of workouts for any level, led by our top-tier personal trainers.  Using the 0-12% incline range and 0-12 MPH speed, your trainers will also automatically adjust your machine to match their movements. After your workout, you can fold up the deck using the SpaceSaver™ design for a convenient storage solution.

longDescription: It’s hard to motivate yourself to go to the gym. The weather might be bad, you may not like to work out in front of other people, or you may be short on time. No more excuses! With the Sportneer Indoor Fluid Bike Trainer, you’ll be able to enjoy a fantastic workout from the comfort of your own home. Whether you’re an experienced cyclist or a complete beginner,this bike trainer stand is just what you need to take your fitness to the next level. This awesome exercise tool holds your bike in place and mimics expensive stationary bike machines. You’ll improve your strength and endurance in no time. The harder you pedal, the more resistance you’ll face. It’ll feel just like a real bike ride!
name: Sportneer - Indoor Fluid Bicycle Trainer Stand - Black and Gray

With the lightweight materials, easy folding, and sleek lines, it will easily fit in any car, train, boat or airplane, so you can keep discovering the world around you. The rollator comes fully assembled and the small organizer bag with shoulder strap is included.

features:
[{'feature': 'BENEFITS:
The Kanjo Memory Foam Foot Mat is a versatile at home solution for general foot pain, neck & back pain, gout relief, and plantar fasciitis relief. Acupressure therapy targets points to reduce pain and relieve tension throughout the body'}, {'feature': 'VELCRO STRIPS.
Kanjo’s mat can be fixed in a rolled position using the velcro strips to serve as a tool for relieving neck & back pain. Kanjo’s foot mat is meant mainly for feet but can be used on body parts such as the back, legs & arms'}, {'feature': 'BUILT IN CARRY STRAP.
The Kanjo Memory Foam Foot Mat is designed with a built in carry strap that makes it easier to travel & experience acupressure therapy on the go'}, {'feature': 'HIGH DENSITY MEMORY FOAM CORE.
Kanjo Acupressure Foot Mat is constructed with premium 3.5lb high density memory foam, molding to the feet and other parts of the body for a custom experience for each user, ensuring a comfortable option for at-home pain relief'}, {'feature': 'BPA-FREE ABS PLASTIC STIMULATORS.
Kanjo’s plastic stimulators are custom designed to ensure maximum coverage on the feet, resulting in the activation of several acupressure points at once. All Kanjo products are FSA and HSA eligible.'}]
longDescription: Taken from ancient Eastern methodologies used in acupuncture, the Kanjo Acupressure Memory Foam Foot Mat targets acupressure points to reduce pain throughout the body. The mat includes a high-density memory foam core that molds to the pained area, providing a custom experience for every user. Though the Kanjo Memory Foot Mat is meant mainly for use on the feet, it can be used on other parts of the body such as the back, legs and arms. The mat can be fixed in a rolled position using the velcro strips which makes the Kanjo Memory Foot Mat a perfect tool for relieving neck and lower-back pain. Utilizing the velcro strips and the built-in carry strap also makes it easy to roll the Kanjo Memory Foot Mat for travel. FSA/HSA eligible
name: Kanjo - Acupressure Memory Foam Foot Mat - Blue

longDescription: AirPop is the world’s first “air wearables” company. Since 2015, we’ve been leveraging anthropomorphic & material science with the latest technology to build ultra-high-performance products that provide an unrivaled breathing experience for millions of users around the world. Comprised of an award-winning team of experts in performance apparel, ergonomics, air filtration, material science, and advanced manufacturing. The foundation of our entire range of masks is class-leading filtration that works 2 ways. Every breath inward through AirPop masks is 97% filtered of particles and droplets and importantly today, every breath outward is filtered just the same. Your Air – Your choice. AirPOP Kids Masks are Kids Size with Grown-Up Performance. Our innovative 3D Air Dome design is engineered for ideal air exchange and reduced CO2 accumulation making breathing so much easier you'll forget your wearing AirPop. Every face is different, so our Kids masks are designed to adapt to different shapes and sizes yet still provide maximum comfort, protection and wearability. All of our masks achieve 97% filtration efficacy with <0.3 micron particles and our masks are conformity assessed again and again to ensure they deliver on our promise and exceed all regulatory requirements. Award Winning Product of the PTPA - Parent Tested Parent Approved Seal. KN95 certified.

Fully controlled by the PowerDot app, it takes the guesswork out of electrical muscle stimulation by guiding and customizing the intensity and pad placement of every treatment session. As a proven Class II FDA cleared medical device, the PowerDot 2.0 is trusted by everyone from the world’s top athletes, to fitness enthusiasts, and beyond.
name: Therabody - PowerDot Duo Smart Muscle Stimulator - Blue

[{'feature': "NO TOUCH DESIGN!

Using the app, you'll get peace of mind in your moment of need with personalized guidance on what to do next with recommendations based on age, fever and symptoms. Know what's wrong and take action in real-time with tips from our in-house clinician!"}, {'feature': 'GREAT FOR EVERYONE
Kids or grandparents! FDA cleared for safety & accuracy, and doctor recommended for all life stages from baby to adult. New moms, parents and growing families trust Kinsa.'}, {'feature': "KEEP YOUR FAMILY HEALTHY.
Understand illness trends in your community to keep your loved ones safe using the HealthWeather map, powered by over 2 million Kinsa smart thermometers. Easily track local illness risk and what's going around."}, {'feature': "IN-APP PROFILES & RECORD KEEPING.
Don't worry about remembering every fever reading or symptom. Assign individual profiles, get medication reminders and recommendations all within the free Kinsa app."}]
longDescription: LIKE A NURSE IN YOUR POCKET We’ve re-imagined the first product you turn to when feeling sick, transforming an ordinary thermometer into a health support tool for the entire family.  This is more than your average forehead thermometer. Take fast, sanitary non-contact temperature readings on multiple family members, but it doesn't stop there. QuickScan links to your smartphone via Bluetooth to help you feel better faster.  Pair your new contactless thermometer with the free Kinsa app to track symptoms and take action in real-time. Using age, fever and symptoms, the app will let you know what to do next - all based on information from our in-house clinician! Do you require rest and fluids, ibuprofen, or a trip to the emergency room?
name: Kinsa QuickScan Non-Contact Thermometer - Blue

longDescription: Wavebalance Wave Balance Blue Light Reducing Glasses protect your eyes from harmful blue light. WaveBalance lenses are designed to filter harmful blue light while allowing beneficial wavelengths, without affecting on-screen colors. Harmful blue light from screens and devices can cause digital eye strain, poor sleep, blurred vision, and even long-term eye damage. Harmful blue light is also emitted by Fluorescent, LED, and Incandescent lighting sources that can be found at homes or in the office. Not all blue light is harmful, some is required for regulate a healthy circadian rhythm. WaveBalance products feature total harmful blue light and 100% UV protection. Frames are designed with comfort in mind and are lightweight. Lenses have premium anti-reflection coatings and are scratch resistant. Packaging is made from 100% recycled PET plastic.
name: Wavebalance Wave Balance Blue Light Reducing Computer and Device Glasses Fashion Blush "Jules", One Size - Blush

longDescription: The Lexie Lumen OTC Hearing Aid includes all the hearing aid features you need at a price you can afford. With advanced battery power, easy-to-control volume settings, crystal clear sound, and access to Lexie Experts 6 days a week, Lexie Lumen allows you to take control of your hearing health! Take control of your hearing with the award-winning Lexie app. Simply connect your hearing aids via Bluetooth to your smartphone and unlock the ability to change volume and environmental settings to suit your hearing needs. Take a hearing check when your hearing aids arrive and your hearing aids will be programmed according to your hearing ability. Easily select the hearing environment from six settings and adjust your devices to your environment. These environments include Everyday Use, Noisy Indoor, Music, Outdoor, Telecoil, and Companion Mic* (*requires a Lexie Companion Mic). You also have access to Lexie Experts through the app, 6 days a week, for free. Don’t settle for anything less than a dual-microphone hearing aid. Lexie’s dual-microphone improves the quality of speech understanding in noisy environments and customizes settings to individual needs. The Directional Hearing microphones amplify the sounds you want to hear and cancel out the sounds you don’t want to hear. Adaptive Noise Reduction allows you to determine if sounds are more speech-like or more noise-like. These features allow you to have the best sound experience. We are not a medical service provider and our products are not a substitute for a visit to a medical professional. It is in your best health interest to consult a physician or healthcare professional before making any medical decisions. PLEASE NOTE: This product is intended for use by adults 18 years of age or older with perceived mild to moderate hearing loss. Any statement made by the product manufacturer or Best Buy in connection with the sale of the hearing aid is not an examination, diagnosis, or prescription by a person licensed to practice medicine and, therefore, must not be regarded as medical opinion or advice. A hearing aid will not restore normal hearing or prevent further hearing loss. Please see the product owner’s guide or visit lexiehearing.com for more information about whether this product is right for you and when you should see a hearing professional.
name: Lexie Hearing - Lexie Lumen OTC Hearing Aids - Bronze

longDescription: The CirC+ by Synca Wellness brings Japanese “Shibui” design into your home, “Shibui” design is subtly beautiful without being flashy, just like the CirC+.  It’s modern furniture-like design hides many features like long rail deep tissue robotic massage technology inside in a tastefully designed exterior.  The CirC+ is rated for users up to 300lbs and uses a full-size massage robot mounted in a long rail SL track frame, this technology ensures you have a relaxing massage from your glutes up to your neck. Unlike other similar chairs if you flip back the head pillow you will receive a deep tissue neck massage that will help melt the stress and tension of the day away.  It’s simple to control using its wireless remote, so you can sit and relax while getting a massage or just using it like a chair.  You can recline back into a relaxing zero gravity position that’s designed to take the pressure off your lower back, which lets the muscles relax, and helps stimulate blood flow.  While in zero gravity add in the gentle hip compressions and lumbar massage therapy and your lower back will feel rejuvenated. The CirC+ lets you enjoy all the benefits of a large massage chair in a tasteful piece of furniture.
name: Synca Wellness - CirC+ Zero Gravity SLTrack Massage Chair - Brown

longDescription: Experience total body tension melting heated massage in the Hisho by Synca Wellness.  The Hisho uses advanced long rail SL-Track massage technology that delivers a superior lower back, glute, and sciatic focused massage while sill delivering the deep tissue relief you need throughout the rest of the back, including your neck and shoulders.  Synca does this by carefully engineering the SL Track system to optimize the quality of massage by following the natural curvature of your back and hips from neck to buttocks while continuously delivering massage.  This is done by gently curving the frame in at meticulously calculated angles near the neck and lumbar region while extending the frame underneath the seat to reach the glutes.  This ensures you receive the largest coverage area of massage possible while also maintaining the highest quality of massage.  The Hisho’s full body compression system makes sure that no part of your body is missed, it’s unique high-rise calf airbags even provide massage coverage in the knees.  The Hisho’s advanced massage technology and zero gravity therapy will leave you relaxed and feeling like you’re sitting on a cloud, try yours today.

longDescription: The Jin 2.0 by Inner Balance is a custom designed robotic massage chair that will provide you with the full body therapeutic massage you need from your head to your toes.  The Jin 2.0 will conduct a body scan measuring the length of your spine and then use its quad headed SL Track massage system to follow the contour of your spine massaging you from your glutes to your neck and everywhere in between.  The Jin 2.0 will utilize 3 unique widths while massaging you to accommodate narrow or broad shoulder widths while delivering full body massage with its total body compression therapy system.  Your arms will be perfectly held in place using its C+U shaped compression system, preventing your arms from slipping out like other massage chairs, while massaging your arms and stimulating blood flow.  The extra-large foot and calf massage system (with foot roller) will expertly and gently massage your foot and calf (of any size legs, slim to large) with ease, and if you’re taller the 6-in extendable leg-rest will glide out to provide extra legroom.  The Jin 2 fits into your home with its zero-wall system, requiring only 2in of clearance behind the chair, and its Bluetooth speakers let you take your massage experience to the next level by enjoying your favorite music.  Once you turn on the therapeutic lumbar heater, you’ll feel a day’s stress and tension melt away and you’ll be relaxed, refreshed, and ready to go!
name: Inner Balance Wellness - Jin 2.0 Heated SL Track Massage Chair - Brown

longDescription: HidrateSpark TAP is the first smart water bottle with Tap To Track Technology. Tap your phone to the bottle to track your daily water intake with the free HidrateSpark App and stay on track with glowing reminders that light up every hour for 12 hours and repeat on your schedule daily. Bottles easily integrate with Apple Health & Google Fit, and connects with Apple Watch, Fitbit and Withings to get the most out of your hydration tracking. The 20 oz stainless steel option is double-wall, vacuum-insulated and keeps drinks cold up to 24 hours without condensation.  Choose between our signature leak-proof Chug or Straw lid options. Each comes  with  a  spout  cover  to  keep  out  dirt  and  germs  and  an  integrated  carry handle that makes it easy to take on-the-go.

longDescription: The HidrateSpark PRO Smart Water Bottle is the world's smartest water bottle! Stainless Steel vacuum-insulated body keeps drinks cold for up to 24 hours, prevents sweating and allows for a pure water taste. Both variations of lids feature a protective spout cover. The Chug lid includes a button lock to prevent accidental spills. This 100% BPA-free bottle includes an easily accessible rechargeable battery on the bottom of the bottle with a fast charging cable so your bottle can always stay charged while you're on-the-go. This new design also includes an improved sensor technology with clinically proven accuracy within 3% of manual readings through Mayo Clinic trials. Using a built-in sensor, the HidrateSpark PRO bottle tracks your water intake and syncs via Bluetooth to the brand’s FREE hydration app on your phone (available on iOS and Android). When a user falls behind on their hydration goal, LED lights embedded in the sensor puck glow in customizable patterns as a reminder to stay on track. Users also receive reminder notifications throughout the day via the hydration app. Perfect as a gift for friends and family—track each other's progress and make staying hydrated a fun activity!
name: Hidrate - HidrateSpark PRO 21 oz. Chug - Brushed SS

longDescription: Beloved by generations since 1962, the Dohm is the original white noise machine. The Uno model features our signature fan-based natural white noise producing the famous Marpac Sound – the soothing ambient sounds of rushing air, without the disturbance of actual moving air or other irritations. With a single-speed option and adjustable tone and volume, the Dohm Uno makes it simple to create a personalized sound environment, excellently masking background sounds and allowing for better sleep, office privacy, effective soothing for kids and babies, and calming for sound-sensitive dogs. Powered by a 6-foot 120V AC plug (for domestic use only), just plug in the Dohm Uno, flip the switch, then rotate the collar to find the best sound for you. Let the noise-masking magic happen for a natural sleep aid, office privacy, baby soothing, tinnitus relief, respite from noisy snorers and unfamiliar hotel rooms, and a relaxing calming balm for barking dogs. The Dohm Uno features a simple and compact design that fits anywhere and blends unobtrusively into surroundings.
name: Yogasleep - Dohm Uno Natural Sound Machine - Charcoal

longDescription: The Enrich Pro ITC utilizes the newest Powered by Lucid patented technology to deliver a more natural sound quality that is superior to traditional “compression” hearing products, providing the wearer better communication in noisy environments as well as enhanced comfort in quiet situations. The result is clear hearing and comfort.  Low-level noise suppression provides for improved comfort in quiet environments. Noises such as air conditioning, refrigerator motors or internal microphone noise are all reduced by this system. This helps keep quiet situations quiet.  Our Dynamic Feedback Canceller employs a patented technique that adapts continuously to changing circumstances while maintaining excellent sound quality. Unwanted feedback is suppressed and stopped without sacrificing sound quality or gain.  Two listening modes to adjust the device to accommodate Conversation and Crowd environments.  Nano Technology coats every aspect of the hearing product at a nanoscopic level and protects much more thoroughly than alternative approaches. The result is a truly durable and invisible liquid repellent coating (inside and out). Our revolutionary Nano-coating does not affect working components, maintaining the look, feel, and functionality of the device.  Lucid Audio’s Enrich Pro ITC employs the latest software to provide greater processing power and increased battery life. Low battery indicating signal alerts user to change batteries prior to complete battery drain.  Includes comfort dome fitting tips to cover a wide range of ear canal sizes.  PLEASE NOTE: This product is intended for use by adults 18 years of age or older with perceived mild to moderate hearing loss. Any statement made by the product manufacturer or Best Buy in connection with the sale of the PSAP is not an examination, diagnosis, or prescription by a person licensed to practice medicine and, therefore, must not be regarded as medical opinion or advice. A PSAP will not restore normal hearing or prevent further hearing loss. Please see the product owner’s guide [or visit https://lucidhearing.com/ for more information about whether this product is right for you and when you should see a hearing professional.
name: Lucid Audio - Lucid Hearing Enrich PRO in The Ear Digital Hearing Amplifier PSAP Pair (Left and Right Ready to Wear) - CLEAR

longDescription: Enlite is an OTC deluxe hearing aid intended for anyone who wants to make their world one click louder. longDescription: Wavebalance Wave Balance Blue Light Reducing Glasses protect your eyes from harmful blue light. WaveBalance lenses are designed to filter harmful blue light while allowing beneficial wavelengths, without affecting on-screen colors. Harmful blue light from screens and devices can cause digital eye strain, poor sleep, blurred vision, and even long-term eye damage. Harmful blue light is also emitted by Fluorescent, LED, and Incandescent lighting sources that can be found at homes or in the office. Not all blue light is harmful, some is required for regulate a healthy circadian rhythm. WaveBalance products feature total harmful blue light and 100% UV protection. Frames are designed with comfort in mind and are lightweight. Lenses have premium anti-reflection coatings and are scratch resistant. Packaging is made from 100% recycled PET plastic.

longDescription: The HidrateSpark PRO Smart Water Bottle is the world's smartest water bottle! Stainless Steel vacuum-insulated body keeps drinks cold for up to 24 hours, prevents sweating and allows for a pure water taste. Both variations of lids feature a protective spout cover. The Chug lid includes a button lock to prevent accidental spills. This 100% BPA-free bottle includes an easily accessible rechargeable battery on the bottom of the bottle with a fast charging cable so your bottle can always stay charged while you're on-the-go. This new design also includes an improved sensor technology with clinically proven accuracy within 3% of manual readings through Mayo Clinic trials. Using a built-in sensor, the HidrateSpark PRO bottle tracks your water intake and syncs via Bluetooth to the brand’s FREE hydration app on your phone (available on iOS and Android). When a user falls behind on their hydration goal, LED lights embedded in the sensor puck glow in customizable patterns as a reminder to stay on track. Users also receive reminder notifications throughout the day via the hydration app. Perfect as a gift for friends and family—track each other's progress and make staying hydrated a fun activity!
name: Hidrate - HidrateSpark PRO 21 oz. Chug - Fruit Punch

longDescription: Inspired by the classic late 60’s eyewear silhouette, the PAISLEY is named after the teardrop-shaped pattern made popular during the era when The Fab Four were getting psychedelic, and the Summer of Love was in full swing. Only difference is now instead of rose-colored glasses, you’ve got blue light protective lenses to keep your focus grounded and your vision clear.
