longDescription: The perfect massage chair that does everything.  The Jin massage chair is the perfect massage chair if you've ever considered this product type before, it has all the features people are asking for while retaining a reasonable price.  The Jin chair offers the major technologies people are asking for such as L Track, Foot Roller, Quad Roller back massage, Multi region heater, Zero gravity, full body air massage, and the ability to fit multiple user body sizes with its special height accommodation technology.  The Jin chair has a couple unique features not found in other chairs that make it stand out to someone that's tried a massage chair before.  It's shiatsu calf massager is a dream and is the perfect balance of shiatsu massage techniques and therapeutic compression massage and its shoulder height adjustment system that lets the chair work for everyone.  The shoulder head adjustment system is innovative and when coupled with the leg extension allows the chair to accommodate taller individuals with ease that have struggled to find chairs that before.  This is the true chair that does everything you want it to, has some unique features, and is still a reasonable cost.  Come try the Jin chair for yourself.

longDescription: Get more from your color treatment with the Remington Pro 1" Flat Iron with Color Care Technology. It features a Heat Control Sensor that, when activated, detects when the flat iron plates are in contact with your hair, and then automatically adjusts temperature to prevent over heating for 2X less damage and 5X longer lasting color. (This feature can be turned on and off.) The 1” floating ceramic plates deliver a smooth glide, with a Ceramic Color-Lock Coating that’s infused with keratin oil, UV filters, and micro-conditioners that lock in a vibrant shine to your styles. Plus, this flat iron includes five digital heat settings and heats up in just 30 seconds so you can quickly create your salon quality finish.
name: Remington - Flat Iron Ceramic Hair Straightener - Gold

[{'feature': 'Advanced medical-grade technology

Setup is easy - simply connect your buds to the free Jabra Enhance app and follow the on-screen instructions to learn how to pair, personalize and program your earbuds to your specific needs.  Jabra Enhance Plus is only compatible with iPhone.'}]
longDescription: Jabra Enhance™ Plus wireless earbuds have been engineered for advanced medical-grade hearing enhancement for your conversations, music, and calls. (iPhone only) As part of GN – the only company in the world with consumer, professional, and medical-grade sound all under one roof – we have a team of expert engineers crafting the world’s leading hearing aids. Now, we’re leveraging that wealth of knowledge to launch our first ever medical-grade hearing enhancement and earbud hybrid. At 40% smaller than our current smallest earbuds*, with four built-in microphones and powerful speakers, these buds are for mild to moderate hearing loss, and specifically engineered to enhance the way you hear everything – from in-person conversations to calls, music, and media. They’re a ground-breaking achievement in miniaturization, 150 years in the making. Now you can focus on what you want to listen to, without just turning up the volume.
name: Jabra - Enhance Plus Self-fitting OTC Hearing Aids - Gold Beige

longDescription: Do what's best for your body. Fitbit Charge 5 + Premium connects the dots between your activity, sleep and stress so you can make the best decisions for your body, mind and health. It all starts with your 6-month Premium membership1 and Daily Readiness2, a score based on activity, sleep and heart rate variability (HRV) that helps you optimize your workout routine. Your score comes with personalized activity recommendations: low means go easy and recover--light yoga, deep breathing--while a high score gives you the green light to go all out. Enhance your recovery routine with advanced stress-management tools like the on-wrist EDA sensor. Stay ahead of heart health with atrial fibrillation (AFib) heart rhythm assessments using the on-wrist ECG app.3 And you'll always have motivation to reach new goals with hundreds of guided workouts, a gallery of refreshing mindfulness sessions plus the fitness features you know and love like Active Zone Minutes and built-in GPS. Fitbit is part of the Google family.

longDescription: The Sharper Image Aromatherapy Neck & Shoulder Wrap combines heat and cooling therapy with aromatherapy for a total spa relaxation experience in a compact package. Relieve muscle stress, pain, and tension, or reduce inflammation, then unwind with the soothing lavender scent. The wrap is made from soft and durable fabric for comfortable relief that lasts. The entire wrap is weighted to promote relaxing pressure stimulation across your neck and shoulders to provide instant relief after a long day. Designed for regular use by one or several persons, the wrap’s unique shape allows it to adapt to any body type. It drapes comfortably around/over the neck and shoulders to apply heat or cold therapy to your muscles (use caution with direct skin contact and heat or cold).
name: Sharper Image - Heated Neck and Shoulder Aromatherapy Wrap, Lavender Scented Hot/Cold - Gray

longDescription: Our proprietary hearing aid technology works by giving you direct sound without compressing or modifying it first. You’ll hear clearer, more natural sounds without distortion and background noise. Unlike other hearing aids, the Engage wireless hearing lifestyle device allows you to stream Bluetooth calls and audio directly from your mobile phone—no need to switch to headphones.  Hear clearly without distortion straight from the box: Stream calls, music and more with Engage hearing aids, the only hearing aid technology available without an audiogram that lets you wirelessly stream Bluetooth from your smartphone so you can seamlessly switch between engaging with your surroundings and taking calls, listening to music, and more without having to transfer to headphones.  With up to 20 hours of battery life and a convenient portable charging case: You never have to worry about your hearing aid batteries – simply recharge them using the wireless carrying case that comes with your pair of Engage hearing aids.  Lucid Hearing mobile hearing app: The Lucid Hearing App is simple to download and provides quick and easy management of your listening experience right from your phone, allowing you to adjust your sound quality, connect you to streaming media, and personalize the way you listen to the world.  Compatible with iPhone: Engage is compatible with iPhone 6s and newer model iPhones running at least iOS 12. If you’re looking for Android compatibility, check out our unique Engage specially designed for Android phones
name: Lucid Hearing - OTC ENGAGE BTE RECHARGEABLE Hearing Aids (iOS) - Gray

features: [{'feature': 'Attenuate sound levels evenly so speech and environmental sounds are clear and natural.'}, {'feature': 'Reduces the risk of hearing damage from loud machinery.'}, {'feature': 'High-Definition response provides greater clarity.'}, {'feature': 'Comfortable, 3-flange fit designed to seal the ear.'}, {'feature': 'Detachable cord to prevent loss.'}]
longDescription: Hearing loss from loud sound affects millions of people, but noise-induced hearing loss is preventable! The Saf-T-Ear 20 dB Noise Reduction Earplugs are ready-fit, high-fidelity earplugs that reduce sound levels evenly while preserving sound quality and clarity. They replicate the natural response of the ear, so sound quality is the same as the original, only quieter. Music and voices are clear-not muffled-making them ideal for concerts, clubs, theaters, aircraft, construction, yard work, airshows, parades, and athletic or motorsports events. The standard size fits most ears. They are reusable, but with repeated use, the ear tips may lose elasticity. For best performance and retention, if you use them frequently, replace them every 3 to 6 months. They are not recommended for use with impulse noises such as gunfire or for sleeping.
name: Lucid Audio - Saf-T-Ears HD 20 dB Reusable Ear Plugs Black 1 pair - GRAY

longDescription: The CirC+ by Synca Wellness brings Japanese “Shibui” design into your home, “Shibui” design is subtly beautiful without being flashy, just like the CirC+.  It’s modern furniture-like design hides many features like long rail deep tissue robotic massage technology inside in a tastefully designed exterior.  The CirC+ is rated for users up to 300lbs and uses a full-size massage robot mounted in a long rail SL track frame, this technology ensures you have a relaxing massage from your glutes up to your neck. Unlike other similar chairs if you flip back the head pillow you will receive a deep tissue neck massage that will help melt the stress and tension of the day away.  It’s simple to control using its wireless remote, so you can sit and relax while getting a massage or just using it like a chair.  You can recline back into a relaxing zero gravity position that’s designed to take the pressure off your lower back, which lets the muscles relax, and helps stimulate blood flow.  While in zero gravity add in the gentle hip compressions and lumbar massage therapy and your lower back will feel rejuvenated. The CirC+ lets you enjoy all the benefits of a large massage chair in a tasteful piece of furniture.
name: Synca Wellness - CirC+ Zero Gravity SL Track Massage Chair - Gray

A breathable cover helps circulate air away from your body, keeping you comfortably cool. For restless sleepers who are looking for a calmer night’s rest! The Casper Weighted Blanket includes beads in individually sewn patches that decrease motion throughout the night, with a fluffy lining to keep you comfortable! The Casper Weighted Blanket is uniquely designed with quilted channels to hug around your body!
name: Casper - Weighted Blanket, 20 lbs - Gray

longDescription: Our Best Seller! Easy to use with simple control over volume and program environment found on the HearingAssist HA-302. Get reliable value with this rechargeable hearing aid. It's designed to help you handle everyday activities with more ease. Customize your environment with 4 programs & 4 volume levels that can be changed with the toggles on the hearing aid body. It features rechargability, directional microphones, a magnetic snap charge dock, advanced digital feedback suppression (whistle), advanced background noise reduction, and crystal clear digital sound. features:
[{'feature': 'Sit closer
Desk-length armrests allow you to sit up close to most desks and tables, while still providing ample, cushioned arm support'}, {'feature': 'Easy rolling mag wheels
Pushed or self-powered with the hand rim, these wheels roll smoothly and easily on airless tires that can’t go flat. Perfect for the user.'}, {'feature': 'Versatile footrests
Flip a lever to swing the footrests aside for getting in, or out, of the wheelchair. Simply lift the footrests to remove them completely.'}, {'feature': 'Folds easily
Lift on the middle of the seat and the chair folds together for easy transport or storage.'}, {'feature': 'Infused with Microban Antimicrobial Protection
Microban antimicrobial* protection is built into the Medline Wheelchair to help prevent stains and odors caused by bacteria, mold and mildew, for the life of the product.'}]
longDescription: This is the wheelchair with all the best features for comfort, convenience, durability and security. The frame is tig-welded steel for strength and durability, and protected by a beautiful, tough powder-coat finish. It rides on smooth rolling, solid, flat-free tires. Comfortable nylon upholstery is easy to keep clean and features antimicrobial protection to help keep your chair fresh and clean by inhibiting the growth of bacteria, mold and mildew continuously. Hemi-height dual axles allow for regular use or foot-power for greater independence. Footrests are easily adjustable and can be swung to the side and locked out of way when needed. Removable desk-length armrests let you sit as close to tables and desks as you like. (This product does not protect users or others against disease-causing bacteria.)
name: Medline Folding Wheelchair with Desk-Length Arms & Swing-Away Legrests, Microban Protection - Gray Frame, Teal Upholstery

features:
[{'feature': 'Who is Wavebalance?
We are a group of dedicated optical professionals on a mission to create best-in-class no-gimmick eyewear that your eyes can trust.'}, {'feature': 'About our lenses
Our lenses are made from premium thickness PC embedded with a proprietary blend of blue light blocking pigments designed to NOT interfere with your on-screen colors. Lenses are compliant with international standards, block 100% of UVA and UVB light, and have lab quality AR coatings.'}, {'feature': 'Frame sizing
52-19-145. What does that mean? Each lens is 52mm wide (left to right) and the distance between the two lenses is 19mm. Nice long temples at 145mm are sure to fit.'}, {'feature': 'Frame Construction
Made from a durable injected acetate, and featuring comfortable spring hinges, these frames are sized to fit most faces.'}, {'feature': 'Not suitable for use as sunglasses.
Clean frames and lenses with mild dish detergent (never use glass cleaner or anything containing ammonia, bleach, or vinegar), and gently pat dry with a clean soft cloth, or let air dry.'}]
longDescription: Wavebalance Wave Balance Blue Light Reducing Glasses protect your eyes from harmful blue light. WaveBalance lenses are designed to filter harmful blue light while allowing beneficial wavelengths, without affecting on-screen colors. Harmful blue light from screens and devices can cause digital eye strain, poor sleep, blurred vision, and even long-term eye damage. Harmful blue light is also emitted by Fluorescent, LED, and Incandescent lighting sources that can be found at homes or in the office. Not all blue light is harmful, some is required for regulate a healthy circadian rhythm. WaveBalance products feature total harmful blue light and 100% UV protection. Frames are designed with comfort in mind and are lightweight. Lenses have premium anti-reflection coatings and are scratch resistant. Packaging is made from 100% recycled PET plastic.
name: Wavebalance Wave Balance Blue Light Reducing Computer and Device Glasses Gradient "Gilson", One Size - Gray to Crystal Gradient

features:
[{'feature': '30% Better Speech Understanding in Noise
HP Hearing PRO hearing aids are clinically proven to deliver a 30% improvement in speech understanding in the presence of noise by simply tapping Focus On in the HP Hearing app.'}, {'feature': 'FDA-Cleared Self-Fitting OTC Hearing Aids with Ear ID™
Ear ID™ measures your hearing levels and delivers personalized hearing amplification calibrated to your unique hearing profile.'}, {'feature': 'Active Noise Cancellation
Intelligent noise control reduces ambient noise levels for immersive audio experiences.'}, {'feature': 'Bluetooth® Streaming
With its large dynamic driver with vented acoustical design, HP Hearing PRO hearing aids stream music and audio with high fidelity from Bluetooth ® connected devices.'}, {'feature': 'iOS and Android Compatibility
The HP Hearing mobile app is compatible with iOS and Android smartphones for wireless control of your hearing aids.'}, {'feature': 'Built-in rechargeable Li-Ion batteries provide up to 8 hours of hearing aid use'}, {'feature': 'Charge case build-in rechargeable Li-Ion battery with up to 32 hours additional charge (included)'}, {'feature': 'Silicone and Foam ear tips provided (1 pair each S, M, L) to fit most ears (included)'}]
longDescription: HP Hearing PRO Self-Fitting OTC Hearing Aids are innovative products that look nothing like a traditional hearing aid. Built to medical device standards and meeting all FDA requirements for safety and efficacy, the HP Hearing PRO features Ear ID™ self-fitting software and technology powered by Nuheara. Ear ID™ has been clinically proven to be substantially equivalent to a professionally-fit hearing aid. The proprietary Ear ID™ software tests the wearer’s individual hearing thresholds from low frequency to high frequency in each ear, then automatically programs the HP Hearing PRO hearing aids for each ear. This ability for the consumer to self-fit through the HP Hearing application, for iOS and Android platform mobile devices, allows a quick and easy acclimation experience for the consumer. The entire acclimation experience takes about 10-15 minutes from unboxing through customization of the user’s personalized profile to accommodate their perceived mild to moderate hearing loss. In addition to the HP Hearing PRO’s capabilities as an OTC hearing aid, this innovative product streams media and phone calls via Bluetooth®. The Active Noise Cancellation minimizes background noise for an immersive sound experience when streaming phone calls or music. Additional features include an HP Hearing app for iOS and Android, Rechargeable built-in Li-ion batteries, and Charge Case for on-the-go charging Most importantly, the HP Hearing PRO has been clinically validated through research completed by the National Acoustic Laboratories to provide a 30% speech understanding improvement in the presence of noise using the directional microphone feature called Focus. This is a significant benefit for consumers in restaurants or social situations where background noise makes understanding speech difficult. Now, at the touch of the HP Hearing app, a wearer can switch the directional microphone settings to Focus on sounds towards their front, quickly allowing for immediate improvement in speech understanding.
name: HP Hearing PRO Self-Fitting OTC Hearing Aids - Grey

longDescription: EnChroma® Colorado Cx3 Sun is our alpine-inspired frame engineered to deliver clear, bright color and 100% UV protection for those with most types of red-green color blindness. With a style worthy of every one of the 55 mountain peaks in the state of its namesake, Colorado is ideal for those who live the sporting life. Features a sleek stainless steel metal frame and generous lens shape wrapped just enough to provide ample protection from UV rays and the elements. Shiny gunmetal color with matte black sculpted, adjustable (TPA) temples and silicone nose pads gives the Colorado universal fit appeal. Pleasing brow curve with angular corners projects a strong look. Each temple tapers at its center for lightness and flairs at the temple end to ensure a secure and comfortable fit. Case included. longDescription: The Avana Beckridge 32-Ounce Stainless Steel Double-Wall Insulated Water Bottle brings together timeless design and effortless utility for everyday hydration. Featuring a patented drinking system including the FreeSip spout—designed for drinking two different ways: sipping upright through the built-in, removable straw or tilting back to swig from the wide-mouth spout opening. Double-wall insulation keeps liquids cold for up to 24 hours or hot for up to 12 hours, and insulates against condensation and heat transfer to the outside, making the bottle suitable for a range of beverages including water, juice, carbonated beverages, tea and coffee. Includes a leak-proof twist cap featuring a retractable carry loop for easy hydration on-the-go. Available in two sizes: 25-ounce or 32-ounce. Rubber foot on the bottom. All materials are BPA and phthalate-free. Hand wash. Manufacturer’s limited lifetime warranty.
name: Avana - Beckridge Insulated Stainless Steel 32 oz. Water Bottle - Gunmetal

longDescription: The iO is Oral-B’s best technology: Clinically Proven 500% More Plaque Removal Along Gumline versus a manual toothbrush. longDescription: The Lexie Lumen OTC Hearing Aid includes all the hearing aid features you need at a price you can afford. With advanced battery power, easy-to-control volume settings, crystal clear sound, and access to Lexie Experts 6 days a week, Lexie Lumen allows you to take control of your hearing health! Take control of your hearing with the award-winning Lexie app. Simply connect your hearing aids via Bluetooth to your smartphone and unlock the ability to change volume and environmental settings to suit your hearing needs. Take a hearing check when your hearing aids arrive and your hearing aids will be programmed according to your hearing ability. Easily select the hearing environment from six settings and adjust your devices to your environment. These environments include Everyday Use, Noisy Indoor, Music, Outdoor, Telecoil, and Companion Mic* (*requires a Lexie Companion Mic). You also have access to Lexie Experts through the app, 6 days a week, for free. Don’t settle for anything less than a dual-microphone hearing aid. Lexie’s dual-microphone improves the quality of speech understanding in noisy environments and customizes settings to individual needs. The Directional Hearing microphones amplify the sounds you want to hear and cancel out the sounds you don’t want to hear. Adaptive Noise Reduction allows you to determine if sounds are more speech-like or more noise-like. These features allow you to have the best sound experience. We are not a medical service provider and our products are not a substitute for a visit to a medical professional. It is in your best health interest to consult a physician or healthcare professional before making any medical decisions. PLEASE NOTE: This product is intended for use by adults 18 years of age or older with perceived mild to moderate hearing loss. Any statement made by the product manufacturer or Best Buy in connection with the sale of the hearing aid is not an examination, diagnosis, or prescription by a person licensed to practice medicine and, therefore, must not be regarded as medical opinion or advice. A hearing aid will not restore normal hearing or prevent further hearing loss. Please see the product owner’s guide or visit lexiehearing.com for more information about whether this product is right for you and when you should see a hearing professional.
name: Lexie Hearing - Lexie Lumen OTC Hearing Aids - Light Gray

longDescription: The Lexie Lumen OTC Hearing Aid includes all the hearing aid features you need at a price you can afford. With advanced battery power, easy-to-control volume settings, crystal clear sound, and access to Lexie Experts 6 days a week, Lexie Lumen allows you to take control of your hearing health! Take control of your hearing with the award-winning Lexie app. Simply connect your hearing aids via Bluetooth to your smartphone and unlock the ability to change volume and environmental settings to suit your hearing needs. Take a hearing check when your hearing aids arrive and your hearing aids will be programmed according to your hearing ability. Easily select the hearing environment from six settings and adjust your devices to your environment. These environments include Everyday Use, Noisy Indoor, Music, Outdoor, Telecoil, and Companion Mic* (*requires a Lexie Companion Mic). You also have access to Lexie Experts through the app, 6 days a week, for free. Don’t settle for anything less than a dual-microphone hearing aid. Lexie’s dual-microphone improves the quality of speech understanding in noisy environments and customizes settings to individual needs. The Directional Hearing microphones amplify the sounds you want to hear and cancel out the sounds you don’t want to hear. Adaptive Noise Reduction allows you to determine if sounds are more speech-like or more noise-like. These features allow you to have the best sound experience. We are not a medical service provider and our products are not a substitute for a visit to a medical professional. It is in your best health interest to consult a physician or healthcare professional before making any medical decisions. PLEASE NOTE: This product is intended for use by adults 18 years of age or older with perceived mild to moderate hearing loss. Any statement made by the product manufacturer or Best Buy in connection with the sale of the hearing aid is not an examination, diagnosis, or prescription by a person licensed to practice medicine and, therefore, must not be regarded as medical opinion or advice. A hearing aid will not restore normal hearing or prevent further hearing loss. Please see the product owner’s guide or visit lexiehearing.com for more information about whether this product is right for you and when you should see a hearing professional.
name: Lexie Hearing - Lexie Lumen OTC Hearing Aids - Metallic Black

longDescription: Polish strands and smooth frizz with the stroke of a brush. features:
[{'feature': "Powerful dual-locking suction cups.
The shower safety bar's suction cups make it convenient and easy to install. No need to hire someone or use any power tools to install the bathroom safety bar."}, {'feature': "Indicates when the bathtub safety bar is properly fastened.
A significant drawback for most suction cup shower handles is not knowing when they're fastened. This can lead to injury. Our tub safety bar features indicators that change from red to green to show when it's properly fastened to the wall."}, {'feature': 'Excellent for travel.
Because no tools are required, the shower safety handle is perfect for travel. Installing and removing the bathtub only takes a few seconds, making it the perfect portable grab bar.'}, {'feature': 'Works on most surfaces.
The shower support bar easily attaches to most surfaces including shower tile and fiberglass. For best results from the shower handlebar, install on a smooth surface.'}, {'feature': 'Available in 12" or 16".
Choose from a more compact 12" bathtub bar or a larger 16" grip bar with more support surface. Smaller bathroom handles are more subtle and fit in more tubs while larger bathtub safety handles offer a larger surface to grab on to.'}]
longDescription: Make getting in and out of the bath safer for your loved ones or patients with the Carex Ultra Grip Xtra 16" Bath Safety Grab Bar. This item makes a smart and convenient addition to your shower. It features a neutral style that blends easily with most decor. This Carex grab bar helps you gain support when entering or leaving the bathtub or shower. It provides an extended 16" surface for added stability and is easy to install; no tools necessary. This bathroom grab bar features a wide handle that is comfortable and easy to grip. The strong suction grips hold tightly to a smooth, flat, and non-porous surface. It has raised edges on the entire surface, offering you a rough area for grasping.
name: Carex Ultra Grip Xtra 16-inch Grab Bar - Multi

features:
[{'feature': 'Controlled wirelessly for comfort.
This physical therapy TENS unit offers wireless pain relief without lead wires getting in the way. The wireless feature makes using it at work, home, or on the go quick, tangle-free, and hidden in plain sight.'}, {'feature': "Can be used with wireless remote or mobile app.
The TENS therapy gives users the option to use it with the wireless remote or mobile app. Perfect for both users that are and aren't tech-savvy. The app is available on both the Apple Store and Google Play."}, {'feature': 'Features TENS, EMS, and Massage Functions.
This multi-use device offers TENS (transcutaneous electrical nerve stimulation) for pain relief, EMS (electrical muscle stimulation) to revive and strengthen muscles, and a massage feature for revival and relation.'}, {'feature': 'Sixteen preset programs and 60 levels of intensity.
Take control of your treatments. The TENS unit machine offers many treatment settings and enables users to increase and reduce the intensity.'}, {'feature': 'Target your treatment area with two electrodes.
The digital TENS unit comes with two wireless electrodes to place on and around the target area. The reusable electrodes conform to your body for a close fit. We recommend replacing them once they lose their stick.'}]
longDescription: Conquer your pain and strengthen your muscles with the AccuRelief Wireless TENS and EMS devices. This 3-in-1 device includes TENS therapy for blocking pain, EMS for muscle recovery, and a massager for relaxation. The OTC TENS unit offers customized treatments with 60 levels of adjustable intensity and 14 preset programs. The home TENS unit is controlled via the remote or through the mobile app found on the App Store or Google Play. This TENS unit muscle stimulator is perfect for targeting various pain types, including back pain, arthritis, sprains, pulls, and more.
name: AccuRelief Wireless 3-in-1 Pain Relief TENS Unit - MULTI

features:
[{'feature': 'Compatible with various TENS units.
The medical-grade TENS electrode kits are compatible with AccuRelief single & dual channel TENS systems and most TENS devices that use snap electrodes.'}, {'feature': "Each pad can be used up to 30 times.
Our TENS therapy replacement pads provide a strong and flexible fit for comfortable wear. They're latex-free, making them safe to use."}, {'feature': 'Easier to attach and detach from the lead wire.
Snap electrodes offer an easier method of attachment to lead wires. The disposable TENS electrode are more comfortable to apply compared to traditional TENS pads.'}, {'feature': 'Includes an electrode placement guide.
Having the proper pad placement is essential for effective treatments. Our placement guide provides illustrations for appropriate TENS EMS electrode pad placement.'}, {'feature': 'Get the OEM original quality.
The electrodes for TENS units are designed to work effortlessly and flawlessly with AccuRelief Single and Dual Channel TENS devices. Replacement and use is quick, easy, and effective.'}]
longDescription: The AccuRelief Universal Supply Kit is designed specifically for use with AccuRelief transcutaneous electrical nerve stimulators (TENS) and electrical muscle stimulators (EMS) units. It has eight sets of two reusable snap electrode pads with two lead wires. The snap electrodes make it easier to attach and detach from the lead wire connection. Lightweight, flexible electrode design shapes to almost any part of the body. Each pad is reusable for up to 30 times. Clinically proven for safe and effective pain relief.
name: AccuRelief TENS Supply Kit With TENS Unit Pads - MULTI

features:
[{'feature': 'Three-channel electric stimulator.
The foot circulation massager features one channel for your feet and two other channels for body stimulation. Use the foot pads for foot pain relief and connect the two lead wires for lower body TENS therapy relief.'}, {'feature': 'Provides powerful prescription-strength relief.
The OTC TENS Unit provides doctor recommended TENS therapy. It helps in relaxing stiff muscles, improves foot circulation, and reduces swollen feet and ankles. Anyone active with foot pain can significantly benefit.'}, {'feature': 'Comes with 15 preset programs.
Customize your pain relief treatment with 15 preset programs. Change the settings until you find a proper mode that helps alleviate your pain.'}, {'feature': 'Comes with everything needed for pain relief.
The TENS therapy device comes with the AccuRelief Ultimate Foot Circulator with Remote, four electrode pads, two lead wires, an adaptor, electrode placement guide, and power supply.'}, {'feature': 'Doubles as a foot massager.
The pain relief device uses EMS (electrical muscle stimulation) technology to act as a foot and leg massager. It helps improve blood circulation in feet, reduce tense muscles and joint pain, and reduce any pain in the lower body and feet.'}]
longDescription: Relax stiff muscles and increase blood circulation with the help of this AccuRelief Ultimate Foot Circulator. It is an advanced electrical stimulator that features a three-channel stimulator for the feet and body. This foot circulation machine provides powerful prescription strength relief through the electrode pads that are placed on your feet or body. It is specially designed to provide you with immediate relief and reduce swollen feet and ankles to help you get back to a normal activity level. Suitable for man and women, this Accurelief foot circulator is ideal for home, office or travel use. It comes with an easy-to-use remote control with 15 preset programs.
name: AccuRelief Ultimate Foot Circulator TENS Unit For Feet - MULTI

longDescription: The Avana Beckridge 32-Ounce Stainless Steel Double-Wall Insulated Water Bottle brings together timeless design and effortless utility for everyday hydration. Featuring a patented drinking system including the FreeSip spout—designed for drinking two different ways: sipping upright through the built-in, removable straw or tilting back to swig from the wide-mouth spout opening. Double-wall insulation keeps liquids cold for up to 24 hours or hot for up to 12 hours, and insulates against condensation and heat transfer to the outside, making the bottle suitable for a range of beverages including water, juice, carbonated beverages, tea and coffee. Includes a leak-proof twist cap featuring a retractable carry loop for easy hydration on-the-go. Available in two sizes: 25-ounce or 32-ounce. Rubber foot on the bottom. All materials are BPA and phthalate-free. Hand wash. Manufacturer’s limited lifetime warranty.
name: Avana - Beckridge Insulated Stainless Steel 32 oz. Water Bottle - Onyx

features:
[{'feature': 'Improve your sleep performance
WHOOP recommends a daily sleep target and provides a detailed view of how much time you spend in every sleep stage. Use Sleep Coach to select the best sleep and wake times and set a vibrating alarm so you wake up ready to perform.'}, {'feature': 'Understand when you’re recovered
By analyzing key metrics that indicate overall health, like heart rate variability (HRV) and resting heart rate (RHR), WHOOP provides you with a daily recovery score to help you understand when you should rest or when you should push yourself.'}, {'feature': 'Track your workouts & optimize your training

Track and log your daily behaviors like diet, alcohol consumption, stress levels, caffeine intake, and more with the WHOOP Journal. WHOOP then calculates which habits help or hurt your sleep and recovery most, making it easier to stick with healthy habits.'}, {'feature': 'Monitor your health
Monitor metrics like heart rate, respiratory rate, resting heart rate, heart rate variability, skin temperature, and blood oxygen levels with Health Monitor. Get alerts when you deviate beyond what’s normal for you, which could be a sign of illness or other factors.'}, {'feature': 'See your long term trends

WHOOP has been validated in lab studies and with third-party testing. 5 LEDs and 4 photodiodes capture your data continuously to deliver best-in-class accuracy.'}, {'feature': 'Style WHOOP your way

longDescription: Available for NEW members, WHOOP is a wearable health & fitness coach that keeps track of everything from your sleep patterns to your exercise habits to not just track what you did, but tells you what to do next. longDescription: Lily Cup One is the most comfortable and easiest to use menstrual cup for newbies and teens! Its petite shape, leak-proof double rim, and removal loop make periods a breeze from start to finish. It even collapses into a carry case the size of a lipstick. Made of ultra-smooth FDA-approved and BPA-free silicone, you won’t feel a thing while it collects your menstrual flow for up to 12 hours of eco-friendly protection. HOW TO USE: Wash your hands before using your Lily Cup. Submerge cup in boiling water for 5-8 min before first use. Fold cup by pushing the front rim of the cup down and in. Angle your cup towards your tailbone and insert it upwards until the ring is inside. Gently squeeze the base of the cup then rotate slightly to create seal. Wear for up to 12 hours and empty 2-3 times per 24 hour period. To remove, sit in a squatting position and bear down. Then grip the removal ring and slowly pull downwards. Squeeze the base to release the seal and pull the stem downwards. Empty fluid into the toilet and wash the cup, reinsert.

longDescription: At Felix Gray, we know that electronic devices are a necessary, and sometimes inevitable, part of our lives. That’s why, at Felix Gray, we offer the hardest-working Blue Light filtering glasses for the hardest-working individuals. Felix Gray filters 15x more of the most impactful Blue Light than any other clear lenses. In doing so, we hope to empower us all to thrive in our modern world. Felix Gray's Roebling is a sophisticated circular frame that works on almost any face shape. The Roebling’s signature keyhole bridge and terrific frame sits perfectly and comfortably on your face. Whether you’re staring at a computer screen for extended periods of time or catching up with late-night reading on your tablet, Felix Gray’s Blue Light filtering glasses are just what you need to relieve symptoms of Digital Eye Strain and support your total well-being. Designed with the modern world in mind, these are our original, proprietary, and virtually clear Blue Light Glasses perfect for everyday wear.

longDescription: HidrateSpark TAP is the first smart water bottle with Tap To Track Technology. Tap your phone to the bottle to track your daily water intake with the free HidrateSpark App and stay on track with glowing reminders that light up every hour for 12 hours and repeat on your schedule daily. Bottles easily integrate with Apple Health & Google Fit, and connects with Apple Watch, Fitbit and Withings to get the most out of your hydration tracking. The 20 oz stainless steel option is double-wall, vacuum-insulated and keeps drinks cold up to 24 hours without condensation.  Choose between our signature leak-proof Chug or Straw lid options. Each comes  with  a  spout  cover  to  keep  out  dirt  and  germs  and  an  integrated  carry handle that makes it easy to take on-the-go.

longDescription: The HidrateSpark PRO Smart Water Bottle is the world's smartest water bottle! Stainless Steel vacuum-insulated body keeps drinks cold for up to 24 hours, prevents sweating and allows for a pure water taste. Both variations of lids feature a protective spout cover. The Chug lid includes a button lock to prevent accidental spills. This 100% BPA-free bottle includes an easily accessible rechargeable battery on the bottom of the bottle with a fast charging cable so your bottle can always stay charged while you're on-the-go. This new design also includes an improved sensor technology with clinically proven accuracy within 3% of manual readings through Mayo Clinic trials. Using a built-in sensor, the HidrateSpark PRO bottle tracks your water intake and syncs via Bluetooth to the brand’s FREE hydration app on your phone (available on iOS and Android). When a user falls behind on their hydration goal, LED lights embedded in the sensor puck glow in customizable patterns as a reminder to stay on track. Users also receive reminder notifications throughout the day via the hydration app. Perfect as a gift for friends and family—track each other's progress and make staying hydrated a fun activity!
name: Hidrate - HidrateSpark PRO 21 oz. Chug - Sea Glass

longDescription: The Lexie Lumen OTC Hearing Aid includes all the hearing aid features you need at a price you can afford. With advanced battery power, easy-to-control volume settings, crystal clear sound, and access to Lexie Experts 6 days a week, Lexie Lumen allows you to take control of your hearing health! Take control of your hearing with the award-winning Lexie app. Simply connect your hearing aids via Bluetooth to your smartphone and unlock the ability to change volume and environmental settings to suit your hearing needs. Take a hearing check when your hearing aids arrive and your hearing aids will be programmed according to your hearing ability. Easily select the hearing environment from six settings and adjust your devices to your environment. These environments include Everyday Use, Noisy Indoor, Music, Outdoor, Telecoil, and Companion Mic* (*requires a Lexie Companion Mic). You also have access to Lexie Experts through the app, 6 days a week, for free. Don’t settle for anything less than a dual-microphone hearing aid. Lexie’s dual-microphone improves the quality of speech understanding in noisy environments and customizes settings to individual needs. The Directional Hearing microphones amplify the sounds you want to hear and cancel out the sounds you don’t want to hear. Adaptive Noise Reduction allows you to determine if sounds are more speech-like or more noise-like. These features allow you to have the best sound experience. We are not a medical service provider and our products are not a substitute for a visit to a medical professional. It is in your best health interest to consult a physician or healthcare professional before making any medical decisions. PLEASE NOTE: This product is intended for use by adults 18 years of age or older with perceived mild to moderate hearing loss. Any statement made by the product manufacturer or Best Buy in connection with the sale of the hearing aid is not an examination, diagnosis, or prescription by a person licensed to practice medicine and, therefore, must not be regarded as medical opinion or advice. A hearing aid will not restore normal hearing or prevent further hearing loss. Please see the product owner’s guide or visit lexiehearing.com for more information about whether this product is right for you and when you should see a hearing professional.
name: Lexie Hearing - Lexie Lumen OTC Hearing Aids - Silver

longDescription: Do what's best for your body. Fitbit Charge 5 + Premium connects the dots between your activity, sleep and stress so you can make the best decisions for your body, mind and health. It all starts with your 6-month Premium membership1 and Daily Readiness2, a score based on activity, sleep and heart rate variability (HRV) that helps you optimize your workout routine. Your score comes with personalized activity recommendations: low means go easy and recover--light yoga, deep breathing--while a high score gives you the green light to go all out. Enhance your recovery routine with advanced stress-management tools like the on-wrist EDA sensor. Stay ahead of heart health with atrial fibrillation (AFib) heart rhythm assessments using the on-wrist ECG app.3 And you'll always have motivation to reach new goals with hundreds of guided workouts, a gallery of refreshing mindfulness sessions plus the fitness features you know and love like Active Zone Minutes and built-in GPS. Fitbit is part of the Google family.
name: Fitbit - Charge 5 Advanced Fitness & Health Tracker - Soft Gold

longDescription: With a variety of unique features to provide an effective, comfortable fit for boys and girls, the Tie Dye Weddingstar Kid's Reusable/Washable Cloth Face Mask with Filter Pocket is ideal for personal use as you venture outside of the home. Made from a soft, breathable cotton fabric, this non-medical face mask includes an adjustable wire nose piece and ear bands. It offers a secure, non-gaping fit, as well as a pocket that can hold a 5-layer carbon filter for more comprehensive protection against particulates, allergens, and pollutants. The disposable filters are sold separately and should be replaced after each use. More environmentally friendly and cost-effective than disposable masks, this inexpensive cloth face covering is machine washable. Worn properly in addition to other preventive measures a cloth face mask is an ideal, affordable precaution to help protect yourself and others.
name: Weddingstar - Kid's Reusable/Washable Cloth Face Mask with Filter Pocket - Tie Dye

longDescription: Whether you’re online for work or for play, staring at a screen can cause intense strain on your eyes. Thankfully, these Insignia NS-PBLBG2T Blue Light Blocking Glasses are perfectly suited to block harmful blue light from affecting your vision. All that and a fun brown tortoiseshell design means these glasses are well-suited for any occasion.

Designed with the modern world in mind, these are our original, proprietary, and virtually clear Blue Light Glasses perfect for everyday wear.

The Uno model features our fan based natural white noise producing our signature sound – the soothing ambient sounds of rushing air, without the disturbance of actual moving air or other irritations. With a single speed option and adjustable tone and volume, the Dohm Uno makes it simple to create a personalized sound environment, excellently masking background sounds and allowing for better sleep, office privacy, effective soothing for kids and babies, and calming for sound-sensitive dogs. Powered by a 6-foot 120V AC plug (for domestic use only), just plug in the Dohm Uno, flip the switch, then rotate the cap and collar to find the best sound for you. Let the noise-masking magic happen for a natural sleep aid, office privacy, baby soothing, tinnitus relief, respite from noisy snorers and unfamiliar hotel rooms, and a relaxing calming balm for barking dogs. The Dohm Uno features a simple and compact design that fits anywhere and blends unobtrusively into surroundings. From Yogasleep, this sleek and stylish Travel Case for Dohm Sound Machines helps you safely bring your sound machine with you wherever you go. The crush-resistant travel case fits perfectly with Yogasleep Dohm Sound Machines and is made from extra-durable EVA material and features a sturdy double-stitched zipper. The protective properties of the outside case safeguards your sound machine from bumps, scratches, and splashes. Features outside carrying loop for travel convenience. Includes an internal mesh pocket for stashing storage cables, product accessories, or anything else.
name: Yogasleep - Dohm Uno + Travel Case - white

longDescription: Hatch Restore combines a smart light, sound machine, sunrise alarm, meditations, and an alarm clock all into one easy-to-use bedside device. It works together with the free Hatch Sleep app to help you personalize a science-backed sleep routine to help you fall asleep, stay asleep, and wake up gently. On top of a rich sound library and 22 light colors, only Hatch Restore makes it easy for you to personalize a bedtime and wake-up routine. It comes with default routine settings based on sleep science, or you can customize them to your liking. A Restore routine is your personal way to fall asleep, stay asleep, and wake up refreshed. In the Hatch Sleep app, you can customize a routine that consists of Read, Wind Down, Sleep and Wake Up steps. Within each step you can personalize light and sound settings to your liking. When you’re ready for bed, just tap the device to start your routine. A sunrise alarm gently wakes you up with light instead of sound. The Restore sunrise alarm mimics a natural dawn, moving from red to orange to white over 30 minutes before your chosen alarm sounds. This gradual exposure to light prompts your brain to release cortisol, the hormone that cues your body to wake naturally and more pleasant. Your routine is fully customizable from your Hatch Sleep app, so you can experiment with different settings for duration, sounds, and light colors. Everybody sleeps better with Hatch.
name: Hatch - Restore Sound Machine, Smart Light and Sleep Sounds - White

longDescription: The CARBON ULTRALIGHT ROLLATOR is a super lightweight rollator. It is recognized for its innovative and unique design by the world-renowned RED DOT design award, and simply a walker that keeps you going - in style! With the lightweight materials, easy folding, and sleek lines, it will easily fit in any car, train, boat or airplane, so you can keep discovering the world around you. The wheels are soft, handles turned for more upright posture, and the brake cables have been hidden inside the frame for a more streamlined look. The rollator comes fully assembled and the small organizer bag with shoulder strap is included.
name: byAcre - Carbon Ultralight Regular Rollator, 16.5" Seat Width, White Frame, Supports up to 285lbs - White

longDescription: AirPop is the world’s first “air wearables” company. Since 2015, we’ve been leveraging anthropomorphic & material science with the latest technology to build ultra-high-performance products that provide an unrivaled breathing experience for millions of users around the world. Comprised of an award-winning team of experts in performance apparel, ergonomics, air filtration, material science, and advanced manufacturing. The foundation of our entire range of masks is class-leading filtration that works 2 ways. Every breath inward through AirPop masks is  97% filtered of particles and droplets and importantly today, every breath outward is filtered just the same. Your Air – Your choice. Designed for everyday use, with a super-light construction  that ensures the mask’s shape doesn’t collapse. It maintains an air cushion between your mouth, nose and lips for comfortable breathing. KN95 certified.
name: AIRPOP - Light SE 4 Pack KN95 Masks - White

features: [{'feature': '✔ SOOTHE ACHY FEET: Take a load off with the Sharper Image Heated Shiatsu Massager! This soft and cozy device uses heat and vibration to relax your sore toes and feet for relief after a long day.'}, {'feature': '✔ ADJUSTABLE STRENGTH: Choose the moderate vibration for a gentle massage. Or, if your feet are extra sore, try the intense setting for a higher strength vibration.'}, {'feature': '✔ LARGE FOOT POCKETS: The spacious pockets are wide and roomy, so you can even wear socks inside without it being too snug. The massager fits up to a men’s size 12 or women’s size 14 feet.'}, {'feature': '✔ NON-SLIP SURFACE: Set the massager on the floor without worries of it moving around. It stays in place without excessive sliding, so you can relax comfortably and securely.'}]
longDescription: Long day spent on your feet? Soothe tense and sore toes with the Heated Foot Massager from Sharper Image! Steady vibration and cozy warmth come together to relieve soreness and tension. If it's just a chilly night and you'd like to warm up your feet, turn on the independent heat function without the vibration. The fleece-lined pockets will heat up and soothe your chilly feet. If you do want to use the massage function, you can choose between two levels of vibration strength: moderate for a gentle massage or intense for very sore feet. Any mom, dad, friend, brother, husband, wife or sister will enjoy the effects of a soothing heated massage! Know someone who spends lots of time on their feet? Or someone who lives in an especially chill climate? Gift them with the heated foot massager-their toes will thank you. And it's sized up to a men's 12 or women's 14 to fit most feet.
name: SHARPER IMAGE Shiatsu Foot Massager - White

longDescription: Turn up the heat for deep relief and soothing indulgence to loosen up tight muscles and relieve soreness and pain. If you are undergoing medical treatment for digestive issues, please consult your doctor to see if this device is suitable for you.'}, {'feature': 'Personalized:
Certain foods can lead to a build-up of gases in the gut, leading to bloating and other discomforts for those with IBS or food intolerances. AIRE enables you to measure gas levels in the gut to track how food is being digested.'}]
longDescription: What’s included? A digestive breath testing device, FoodMarble app, and 6-Week Discovery Plan and Food Intolerance Testing Kit to give you the complete FoodMarble experience.  What is it? The FoodMarble AIRE and connected app help find the foods that work for your digestive system by measuring hydrogen levels on your breath. Based on leading gut health research and technology, we’ve created the world’s first personal digestive tracker.  How does it work? The FoodMarble AIRE uses the same breath testing technology as hospitals, but in a pocket sized device. When food isn’t digested fully, the bacteria in your gut break it down and this can release hydrogen. The hydrogen is absorbed into your blood before transferring to your breath via your lungs. Breath testing measures the levels of hydrogen in your gut, to help you find the foods that are right for you. Your digestion is unique to you. That’s why finding out what’s causing your symptoms can feel like guesswork. FoodMarble AIRE is designed to help you find the foods that work with your digestive system, so you don’t have to guess anymore.
name: FoodMarble AIRE Bundle - Food intolerance breath test device, including a FODMAP testing kit and 6-week Discovery Plan. - White

Easily use the wrap as a hot pack by heating it in a microwave for warm moist heat therapy. Its therapeutic features work great to increase blood flow, relieve pain, and aid in healing any pain or injuries.'}, {'feature': 'Doctor recommended moist heat for pain relief.
Moist heat therapy is proven to be more effective over dry heat. It can help reduce pain in just two hours compared to eight with dry heat.'}, {'feature': 'Provides both hot & cold therapy.
For anyone looking to use contrast therapy, the Bed Buddy Hot n Cold Wrap is the perfect solution. Use it as a heat pack to reduce swelling or as a cold pack to aid recent injuries. Throw it in the microwave for heat or in the freezer for cold therapy.'}, {'feature': "Flexible form-fitting design.
To be highly effective, heat and cold packs need to conform to the body. We've designed our hot and cold packs with a form-fitting design to fit the area needing aid. This design ensures you'll get the most out of your Bed Buddy Wrap."}, {'feature': "Reusable and washable.
We've designed the Bed Buddy Hot & Cold Wrap for continuous use. To wash it, use a wet rag or wipe to clean it."}]
longDescription: The versatile Bed Buddy Thermatherapy Wrap can be used for alternating ice and heat therapy. It provides doctor-recommended moist heat to help ease sore muscles, aches, and pains. It comfortably conforms to the body, even when cold. Bed Buddy is both safe and straightforward to use and is filled with 100% natural grains, herbs, and flowers. Use it as a natural alternative or compliment to over-the-counter drug treatments.
name: Bed Buddy - Hot And Cold Microwaveable Neck Wrap - White

longDescription: The Sharper Image SpaStudio Vanity Plus Mirror includes 3 swing-out trays that hold makeup and other necessities to keep your counter area clean and organized. The trays all neatly close to provide a clean aesthetically pleasing look for any bathroom, desk, or countertop. The distortion-free mirror tilts securely into place and has a 5X zoom on the backside to ensure you always get the best view of yourself. The mirror also includes a small 10X magnetic mini mirror to ensure every inch of your face is flawless. The mirror features a bright LED halo light ring that can be adjusted with the touch of a finger. Simply place your finger on the sensor to turn the light on and then slide it left or right to adjust the brightness levels for optimal lighting.
name: Sharper Image Spastudio Vanity Plus 10-Inch LED Mirror with Storage - White

longDescription: The Carex Deluxe CPAP Chinstrap and chin restraint presents an ideal solution for those who may experience problems associated with open mouth-breathing during sleep therapy. Over time CPAP headgear and chinstraps may need occasional replacement as they become stretched or lose elasticity over time. For optimal comfort and effectiveness of your CPAP treatment, purchase a new chinstrap for your mask today.  One size fits most. Hook and loop straps give users a way to adjust until the sleep apnea headgear is at a comfortable fit. The one-size-fits-most design makes the snoring head strap comfortable and easy to use.  Soft, breathable fabric provides a relaxed but firm fit. The CPAP chin strap's breathable fabric lets your skin breathe without absorbing sweat and becoming uncomfortable. Its relaxed yet firm fit offers a new level of comfort in anti-snoring chin straps.  Features a chin cut-out to relieve tension.  The chin strap for sleeping features an apnea chin strap cut-out to cushion the chin without applying too much pressure or leaving marks. The sleep apnea head straps chin cut-out provides an extra level of comfort for better sleep.  Helps stop snoring. Snoring can inhibit you from getting a good night's rest. The chin strap for snoring properly keeps your mouth closed to prevent snoring. If you're looking for a chin strap to stop snoring, this is it.  Works in unison with CPAP machines. The sleep apnea strap's adjustable feature makes it an excellent chin strap for CPAP machines. You won't have to worry about the sleep apnea chin strap interfering with your CPAP equipment.  Not made with natural rubber latex. Latex can irritate the skin and further hinder you from sleeping. Our sleep apnea jaw strap provides a safe and effective method for a good night's sleep.  Includes one 34.5" x 1 1/8" attractive ruby red strap
name: Carex - Deluxe CPAP Chinstrap - White

Stylish, insulated stainless-steel water bottle with straw for hot and cold beverages.'}, {'feature': 'FreeSip Spout

longDescription: The Avana Ashbury 18-Ounce Stainless Steel Double-Wall Insulated Water Bottle brings together timeless design and effortless utility for everyday hydration. Featuring a patented drinking system including the FreeSip spout—designed for drinking two different ways: sipping upright through the built-in, removable straw or tilting back to swig from the wide-mouth spout opening. Double-wall insulation keeps liquids cold for up to 24 hours or hot for up to 12 hours, and insulates against condensation and heat transfer to the outside, making the bottle suitable for a range of beverages including water, juice, carbonated beverages, tea and coffee. Includes a leak-proof twist cap featuring a flexible carry loop for easy hydration on-the-go. Available in two sizes: 18-ounce or 24-ounce. All materials are BPA and phthalate-free. Hand wash. Manufacturer’s limited lifetime warranty.
name: Avana - Ashbury Insulated Stainless Steel 18 oz. Water Bottle - White

longDescription: Introducing the Panasonic nanoe salon Hair dryer with oscillating quick-dry nozzle EH-NA67-W (white)—the hair dryer that lets you achieve a healthy, radiant look every day, with no hot spots as you dry. A unique oscillating dryer head disperses heat evenly, making sure you are in ultimate comfort. Moisture-infusing nanoe technology hydrates hair by gently infusing nanoe particles, which hold 1000x more moisture than regular ions, into every shaft of hair so you can dry hair without drying it out. The nanoe salon Hair dryer is perfect for the whole family, whether you need an easy-breezy blow dry or more advanced, salon-level styling from home. The included diffuser attachment helps you keep curls and waves healthy and hydrated, and a concentrator attachment allows for a direct stream of air.
name: Panasonic - EH-NA67-W Nanoe Hair Dryer with Oscillating QuickDry Nozzle - White

longDescription: The TheraFace PRO is your all-in-one solution for optimal facial health. TheraFace PRO goes where no facial device has gone before, bringing Therabody’s renowned technology behind percussive therapy to the face to reduce tension, relax facial muscles, and care for it at the deepest level. Offering more science-backed facial therapies than any other — the TheraFace PRO also features skin-toning microcurrent therapy , rejuvenating light therapy and a revolutionary new way to more deeply cleanse the face. And because every face is unique, we engineered the most personalized experience possible with an easy-glide magnetic ring system that allows you to seamlessly switch between, and even combine, treatments. As your needs change, the TheraFace PRO changes with you. It’s time to go beyond beauty, because true facial health is more than skin deep.

longDescription: 3M Particulate Respirator 8210, N95 is a disposable particulate respirator that is designed to help provide reliable respiratory protection of at least 95 percent filtration efficiency against certain non-oil based particles. This respirator is designed for use for particles such as those from grinding, sanding, sweeping, sawing, bagging, or other dusty operations. This respirator can also help reduce inhalation exposures to certain airborne biological particles (examples: mold, Bacillus anthracis, Mycobacterium tuberculosis), but cannot eliminate the risk of contracting infection, illness, or disease. The respirator incorporates 3M’s proprietary technology with advanced electrostatically charged microfiber filter media designed for ease of breathing. This respirator is compatible with a variety of protective eyewear and hearing protection.
name: 3M - Particulate Respirator N95 Masks - 20 pack - White

longDescription: Experience the elegance of Japanese engineering.  The Kagra’s 4D Japanese engineered massage robot is powered by a 2nd generation software that utilize 78 massage techniques enhanced with specialized stretch software.  The stackable layered stretch programs allow the user to enhance their massage experience with a targeted deep stretch massage enabling the user to target and stretch key body parts such as the neck, chest, hip, legs, and lower back.   Beyond the amazing massage you’ll have all the bells and whistles you want to enjoy such as the wireless Bluetooth audio system, pulsing shiatsu foot massage, finger tips controls, precision neck massage, triple region heat system, and zero gravity massage.  You can even sit back and relax and not worry about your pets crawling under the chair as it’s pet shield lets your sit worry free.  You’ll be able to stow the foot massage portion using the reversible ottoman and use the chair like your favorite recliner and stream your Bluetooth enabled tv’s audio through the chair while you relax worry free.  Get your new favorite recliner today in the Kagra by Synca Wellness. SYNCA WELLNESS IS THE FUTURE OF MASSAGE CHAIRS ™

longDescription: Everything-proof your mattress. Keep your mattress looking and feeling brand new by guarding against dirt, spills, and normal wear and tear. The best mattress protectors match utility with comfort. You don’t want anything that squeaks or smells, but you need a quality mattress protector that actually protects you and your bedding. To meet these standards, a waterproof mattress cover should use a material that’s liquid-proof and breathable—like Casper’s thermoplastic sheeting. Additionally, full and fitted coverage is crucial. Unlike a waterproof mattress topper, covers need to guard all exposed surfaces (top, sides, and at least partial bottom). We use a clinging stretch design that never slides or shifts, providing maximum waterproof protection.
name: Casper - Waterproof Mattress Protector - White

features: [{'feature': 'Anti-microbial'}, {'feature': 'Electronic safe'}, {'feature': 'Designed for convenience'}, {'feature': 'Designed to dissolve ear wax'}, {'feature': 'Designed to remove bacteria that can cause irritation and infection'}]
longDescription: Professional audiologist quality cleaning and care products for your ears and for all hearing aids, earphones or wearables. Made in France. Hearing Assist’s pre-packaged Cleaning Wipes provide the utmost convenience for cleaning your hearing aids on the go. Our cleaning wipes are soaked in a solution that allows for a complete cleaning of hearing aids by dissolving ear wax and removing bacteria, all without damaging the electronics or the color of your device. longDescription: iO5 is clinically proven to clean teeth & healthier gums 100% in one week versus a manual toothbrush. The i05 coaches you to a perfect clean with a "Smart Display". Personalized coaching and an accompanying App is on your team for your everyday brushing task. A rounded head and gentle micro-vibrations with the magnetic interaction delivers smooth, harmonious motion through a synchronized cleaning action (micro-vibrations synced with oscillations). A Built-in two-minute timer ensures an even easier experience, helping you get an optimal clean on all your teeth. The timer provides four 30-second intervals to clean each quadrant of your mouth. We keep the time, so you don’t have to. Delivering the perfect pressure is done by having a pressure sensor. The pressure sensor Indicates optimal cleaning pressure and warns of over pressure. Complete with an accompanying travel case, you’ll have a fresh clean everywhere you go. Best of all, it is brought to you by Oral-B the #1 brand used by dentists worldwide.
name: Oral-B - iO Series 5 Rechargeable Electric Toothbrush w/Brush Head - White

features:
[{'feature': 'Better Sleep. Backed by science
Backed by science to help you fall asleep faster and enhance the quality of your sleep, SmartGoggles are a safe and natural sleep solution.'}, {'feature': 'Personalized Relaxation
SmartGoggles are the only device with SmartSense, a proprietary technology that uses your biometric data to optimize your experience.  The SmartRelax mode uses personalized vibration to lower your heart rate.'}, {'feature': 'More Modalities for More Customization
SmartGoggles combine heat, targeted vibration, and soothing massage with dedicated modes for focus, relaxation, and sleep. Settings, intensity and temperature can be adjusted for everyone’s specific needs.'}, {'feature': 'SmartSense Technology
Powers SmartRelax mode to physically lower your heart rate and help reduce stress and anxiety.'}, {'feature': '3 modes: Focus, SmartRelax and Sleep for custom mind and body wellness
Multiple modalities– vibration, massage, heat – tailored to provide relaxation for the eyes and face and relief for headaches and migraines.'}, {'feature': 'Portable, foldable design for relaxation wherever you go.'}, {'feature': 'Designed for use with the Therabody app to deliver an integrated holistic wellness solution.'}]
longDescription: A smart wearable that helps ease facial tension and headaches during the day and helps you relax and sleep at night. Whether you stare at a screen all day, suffer from headaches and migraines, or struggle to fall asleep, Therabody SmartGoggles keep you moving throughout your day and help you rest at night. Slip them on to help ease facial tension, relieve eye strain, decrease headache pain and calm your body and mind. Using our exclusive Smartsense Technology™, the SmartRelax mode measures your heart rate to personalize your experience. Our Focus and Sleep modes use a combination of heat, vibration, and massage to help with concentration and rest. Pair SmartGoggles with the Therabody  app for a multi-sensory experience that supports sleep, focus, relaxation and more.
name: Therabody - Smart Goggles - White

longDescription: Get 14 biometrics and encouraging messages every time you weigh in with the Etekcity Apex HR Smart Fitness Scale. Connect the scale to the free VeSync app to view complete results, see progress graphs, and set goals. Customize the scale’s colorful display by selecting and organizing which 7 biometrics you’d like to see after every weigh-in, so what’s important to you comes first. Baby Mode allows you to hold your baby or pet while weighing them, taring your weight from theirs. Zero-Current Mode turns off the electrical current, creating a safe weighing experience for pregnant users or those with implanted medical devices. Connect to voice assistants, sync data with other fitness apps, and create unlimited user profiles.
name: Etekcity Apex HR Smart Fitness Scale - White

longDescription: Make your bed a luxurious getaway. Upgrade your tired, scratchy sheets to the ultimate in comfort with GhostSheets, featuring the extreme resilience of Supima cotton and the luxurious, cooling comfort of TENCEL fibers. If you’ve been searching for the perfect luxury sheets but can’t seem to find them, we know the feeling. Ever purchased cozy sheets that start pilling after one wash? Ever caved to marketing ploys that push thread count over everything else, only to find yourself sorely disappointed? You’re not alone. At GhostBed, we care about quality—not thread count. And our GhostSheets can walk the walk, and talk the talk.

features:
[{'feature': 'The Solution for a Peaceful Sleep Environment
Stay asleep through all kinds of unwanted disturbances up to 35dB. Ear wings and Twin Seal ear tips create a secure seal to block sound while the exclusive algorithm dynamically adjusts audio volume in response to external noise levels.'}, {'feature': 'Comfortable, Even for Side Sleepers
The slim, light, and compact design keeps Sleep A10 snugly in your ears without protruding. Wear them all night long without any discomfort and wake up feeling refreshed and ready for the day.'}, {'feature': 'Choose Your Favorite Sleep Audio Program
The soundcore app offers a wide variety of white noise and soothing sleep specific audio  to help you sleep and relax. Or connect Sleep A10 by Bluetooth 5.2 to listen to audio from your favorite apps.'}, {'feature': 'Customized for Sleep Sounds
​​Customized dynamic drivers with titanium and ceramic diaphragms enhance low frequencies and the calming effect of white noise and other sleep-inducing sounds to help you fall asleep faster.'}, {'feature': "Track Your Sleep
Monitor your sleep status and get feedback on the duration and quality of sleep.  Sleep A10 automatically pauses audio once you've fallen asleep, and you can set a personal alarm to avoid disturbing anyone else."}, {'feature': "Passive Noise Masking
Sleep A10's cleverly designed flexible ear wings and Twin Seal ear tips create a comfortable secure seal for enhanced passive noise blocking."}, {'feature': 'Adaptive Noise Masking
The noise masking algorithm detects external noise levels and automatically adjusts audio volume to keep your surroundings from disrupting your sleep.'}, {'feature': "All-night Comfort
​​Built to be comfortable even for side sleepers, Sleep A10's slim, lightweight, and compact earbuds are practically unnoticeable for all-night wear."}, {'feature': 'Listen to Your Favorite Content
Listen to soothing sleep sounds from the selection on the soundcore app, or connect Sleep A10 via Bluetooth 5.2 to other devices to listen to audiobooks, podcasts, and other relaxing content.'}, {'feature': "Smart Switch
When turned on, the earbuds will automatically switch from Online mode to Sleep mode and stop playing audio when they detect that you've fallen asleep."}, {'feature': 'In-Ear Alarm
Set a personal alarm in the app to wake yourself up without disturbing your partner.'}, {'feature': "Up to 10-Hour Playtime
A single charge lasts a whole peaceful night and the case recharges Sleep A10 once you've woken up."}]
longDescription: Soundcore Sleep A10 Earbuds are your perfect companion for a peaceful night's sleep.  They’re designed around an exclusive 4-Point Noise Masking system to keep night-time disturbances under your radar. Enhanced passive noise canceling combines with an advanced active noise masking algorithm, and soothing sleep sounds to block out up to 35dB of unwanted noise and deliver the ideal sleep environment. Sleep A10 earbuds are tiny and lightweight so they stay comfortably in your ears, all night long. Slim profile and pressure-free fit means even heavy side-sleepers can rest the entire night without discomfort or fatigue.
name: Soundcore Sleep A10 Earbuds - White

longDescription: Treat your skin to a cold steam treatment with the Nano Sprayer! With its Nano high-speed vibration technology, the steamer splits water molecules into tiny nanometer particles, instantly producing ultra-fine nano ionic steam that effectively penetrate deep into the skin, moisturizing your skin and leaving it smooth, supple and hydrated. The cooling function shrinks the pores and relieves skin irritation. Each session generates one minute of nano mist, sufficient to rejuvenate and hydrate the skin. It also provides necessary humidity to set and refresh your makeup. The cool steam treatment can be used on the face, hair, neck, chest, hands, arms and other areas. Relax and rejuvenate after just 60 seconds of usage! A pocket size travel bag is included for your convenience.
name: Kingdom Cares - Cool Nano Mist Facial Sprayer - White

longDescription: The Hot Mist Nano Steamer takes advanced PTC ceramic heating to vaporize water, producing visibly strong steam instantly through high frequency ultrasonic vibration, to open pores and absorb moisture. The ultra-fine Nano ionic steam effectively penetrates deep into the skin, providing a better hydrating effect and leaving the skin smooth, supple and hydrated. The UV lamp sterilizes steam so that it can reach your skin in the purest, most effective condition. The hot steam effectively opens pores and helps remove trapped dirt and dead skin, promotes the regeneration of collagen for smooth and tender skin, and improves absorption of your favorite beauty creams.
name: Prospera - Hot Mist Nano Facial Steamer - White

longDescription: Advanced Nano Technology- the Facial and Hair Steamer is a 2-in-1 hair and skin care unit. The steamer is composed of a clear water tank and a 360 degree adjustable nozzle. An aroma pad can be placed on the nozzle for a different user experience, and the Ion function can be turned on or off. The hair cap is large enough to accommodate any head size and is easy to use and assemble. For Face: The ultra-fine Nano ionic steam effectively penetrates deep into the skin, providing an enhanced hydrating effect and leaving the skin smooth, supple and hydrated. For Hair: The steamer moisturizes and hydrates scalp and hair, preventing breakage and split ends; it also improves absorption of conditioners and other treatments. There is a built-in ozone generator as well as a controlled release of negatively charged oxygen which helps reduce itchiness and prevents dandruff.
name: Prospera - Hot Mist Nano Facial and Hair Steamer - White

longDescription: Our polyester down-alternative pillow uses materials that are lightweight and airy, so every night feels like sleeping on a cloud. The synthetic fill is hypoallergenic, designed for those sensitive to down or who prefer pillows with the light support of down over the weighty bounce of foam. Best for back sleepers and side sleepers. Our down alt pillow sets are available in standard size and King size.
name: Tuft & Needle - Down Alternative Pillow 2 Pack - Standard - White

longDescription: We built a machine-washable mattress cover to complement the best attributes of our mattresses, from heat dissipation to a snug fit. We topped the waterproof protective film with a soft, comfortable cover to mimic the feel of our mattress. The fitted-sheet style of our mattress protector fits mattresses up to 14 inches and allows for easy removal when you’re ready to wash.
name: Tuft & Needle Mattress Protector - Twin - White

features: [{'feature': 'THE ORIGINAL SOUND MACHINE\nBeloved by generations since 1962, the Dohm model features our fan-based natural white noise producing our signature sound – the soothing ambient sounds of rushing air, without the disturbance of actual moving air.'}, {'feature': 'With two-speed options for adjustable tone and volume, making it simple to create a personalized sound environment, excellently masking background noise and allowing for better sleep, office privacy, effective soothing for kids and babies, and calming for sound-sensitive dogs.'}, {'feature': 'Assembled for decades in the USA and backed by a one-year limited warranty and the always exceptional Yogasleep customer service promise, we stand behind each product and offer you a 101 night trial to try it out.'}, {'feature': 'Noise-masking magic for a natural sleep aid, office privacy, baby soothing, tinnitus relief, respite from noisy snorers and unfamiliar hotel rooms, and a relaxing calming balm for barking dogs.'}, {'feature': 'Featuring a new, intuitive Michael Graves design, the Dohm is available in charcoal, or white with accents in blue, pink, green, or gray.'}]
longDescription: Beloved by generations since 1962, the Dohm is the original white noise machine. The Dohm model features our fan-based natural white noise producing our signature sound – the soothing ambient sounds of rushing air, without the disturbance of actual moving air or other irritations. With two-speed options for adjustable tone and volume, the Dohm makes it simple to create a personalized sound environment, excellently masking background sounds and allowing for better sleep, office privacy, effective soothing for kids and babies, and calming for sound-sensitive dogs. Powered by a 6-foot 120V AC plug (for domestic use only), just plug in the Dohm, flip the switch to high or low, then rotate the cap and collar to find the best sound for you. Let the noise-masking magic happen for a natural sleep aid, office privacy, baby soothing, tinnitus relief, respite from noisy snorers and unfamiliar hotel rooms, and a relaxing calming balm for barking dogs. From Yogasleep, this sleek and stylish Travel Case for Dohm Sound Machines helps you safely bring your sound machine with you wherever you go. The crush-resistant travel case fits perfectly with Yogasleep Dohm Sound Machines and is made from extra-durable EVA material and features a sturdy double-stitched zipper. The protective properties of the outside case safeguards your sound machine from bumps, scratches, and splashes. Features outside carrying loop for travel convenience. Includes an internal mesh pocket for stashing storage cables, product accessories, or anything else.
name: Yogasleep - Dohm + Travel Case - White & Gray

longDescription: Your blowout just got personal with the new T3 AireBrush Duo hot air brush. This Allure Best of Beauty winner takes your style from smooth and sleek to bouncy and wavy with the simple swap of a brush. Featuring a powerful built-in ion generator and a smart microchip, T3 IonFlow Technology delivers an ion-enriched airstream and precise, digitally controlled heat for polished, frizz-free results. The T3 AireBrush Duo features an interchangeable brush design with two brush attachments and 15 heat and speed combinations for personalized styling. Choose the round brush attachment for bold, voluminous looks or the paddle brush attachment to stretch and smooth coily hair types and straighten and polish straight, wavy and curly hair types. SmoothGrip Bristles deliver optimal tension and styling control for effortless styling, while a CeraGloss ceramic surface imparts shine. This powerful blow dry brush delivers shiny, beautiful results for every hair type. Swap, set, style!
name: T3 - AireBrush Duo Interchangeable Hot Air Blow Dry Brush with Two Attachments - White & Rose Gold

longDescription: Tailor your heat for smooth, shiny results and less damage. Introducing the first-of-its-kind professional flat iron that delivers styling personalization like never before. Smooth ID uses advanced T3 Heat ID Technology to reimagine your styling experience. A smart-touch interface and 9 heat settings automatically adjust to your unique profile, based on hair texture, length and color treatments. Eliminate the guesswork with personalized heat that delivers smooth, shiny results. Engineered with T3 Rapid HeatIQ Technology, Smooth ID ensures advanced heat precision for frizz-free, one-pass results. CeraGloss ceramic plates smooth the hair cuticle and lock in shine, while an ion generator infuses millions of frizz-smoothing negative ions. Use the Refresh Mode for second-day retouches with less heat exposure to help protect your hair. Designed with ThermaTouch insulation technology for superior grip comfort so you can style with confidence.
name: T3 - Smooth ID 1 Smart Flat Iron with Touch Interface - White & Rose Gold

The T3 SinglePass Curl collection delivers long-lasting curls for every hair type and any style.
