The SinglePass Curl 1 ¼” delivers curls that keep up.

longDescription: Less time. Less frizz. More hydration. Your superior drying experience has arrived. The T3 AireLuxe professional hair dryer features a custom-engineered fan that propels a 128% wider airflow* to significantly reduce dry time, while enveloping hair in a gentle airstream designed to help retain 60% more of its natural moisture.** A powerful ion generator infuses hair with 10 million negative ions per second to banish frizz and boost shine, and a smart microchip digitally controls 15 heat and speed settings for minimized heat exposure, reduced damage*** and personalized styling for every hair type. Now 30% quieter, T3 AireLuxe is compatible with four different attachments**** to create a variety of looks that last. Hydrated, frizz-free hair has never been this easy—or this fast.
name: T3 - AireLuxe Professional Hair Dryer - White & Rose Gold

longDescription: AirPop is the world’s first “air wearables” company. Since 2015, we’ve been leveraging anthropomorphic & material science with the latest technology to build ultra-high-performance products that provide an unrivaled breathing experience for millions of users around the world. Comprised of an award-winning team of experts in performance apparel, ergonomics, air filtration, material science, and advanced manufacturing. The foundation of our entire range of masks is class-leading filtration that works 2 ways. Every breath inward through AirPop masks is  97% filtered of particles and droplets and importantly today, every breath outward is filtered just the same. Your Air – Your choice. Designed to move with you. Engineered Airknit delivers advanced comfort, superior breathability and lightweight protection. The most advanced technical textile ever developed for a mask. Specific zones of high airflow are made possible through a combination of engineered knitting and compression forming. The result is our lightest weight, most breathable mask ever. Includes 4 replaceable filters.

longDescription: If lower back pain or hip discomfort keeps you awake a night, The Mind Reader Memory Foam Pillow is the solution you’ve been searching for. The foam pillow can help alleviate your pain. The knee pillow is ergonomically designed to fit comfortably between your legs and provide ideal spinal alignment and support that helps reduce sciatica, lower back, and hip or joint pain. Having back or knee pain can keep you tossing and turning all night long and can interrupt the overall quality of sleep. Poor alignment, joint & back pain are just a few causes of unhealthy sleep. Using the Mind Reader Knee Pillow, you can improve and eliminate multiple problem areas in your body and finally feel well rested. The knee pillow is designed with a zippered cover that ensure the pillow does not get too warm and is machine washable for easy and simple cleaning. Simply throw it in the washing machine with your whites and it will come out clean as ever making it convenient even for the messiest users. Our knee pillow cushion comes with a handle that allows you to carry this item anywhere you need it to be. Take it with you on a plane, on the train, or even on the bus for your daily commute. 100% high-density cut memory foam is durable and provides long-lasting comfort and is far more superior than the competitors.  Color: White Material: Memory Foam
name: Mind Reader - Orthopedic Knee Pillow Sciatica Relief

longDescription: As DUDES we are dirty, sweaty and disgusting humans. Access to a shower is not always a realistic option after every awesome, stanky, or highly questionable situation. Have no fear, now it’s time to embrace those moments. The DUDE Shower gives you a fast and effective way to remove all sort of nasty DUDE stank and stay fresh on-the-go. Our large size body wipes are thick like washcloths, fragrance free and infused with soothing aloe and vitamin-e. Use it wherever and whenever. Why Dude Shower? Our extra thick and extra large disposable body wipes are the ultimate solution to all of your stank problems. Use a few to clean your entire body when showering is not an option. Dude Shower is a quick drying wipe that leaves no sticky feeling or residue behind.
name: DUDE PRODUCTS - DUDE Shower Wipes 8ct Dispenser Pack

features:
[{'feature': 'First Launch Monitor of its Kind
Golf’s first portable and affordable Launch Monitor and Golf Simulator'}, {'feature': 'Launch Monitor like no Others
SkyTrak is a launch monitor and golf simulator combination designed to act as a game improvement tool while you practice or play virtual golf'}, {'feature': 'High Speed Photography
High-speed photography captures the golf ball and provides an accurate reading with measurable parameters that include ball speed, distance (carry and total), launch angle, club speed, spin rates'}, {'feature': 'Just Like at the Driving Range
Driving Range functionality allows golfers to practice on a virtual driving range with real-time data and accuracy with instant 3D visualization of the ball flight'}, {'feature': 'Unit is Portable
SkyTrak is a compact unit that wirelessly connects to compatible devices and displays shot data and ball flight visual feedback as soon as you hit the ball'}, {'feature': 'Use Rain or Shine
Tee it up, rain or shine, 365 days a year, in the convenience of your own home'}, {'feature': 'Improve Your Golf Game
Open up a new world of game improving practice and hours of entertainment away from the course'}, {'feature': 'Battery Powered
Built-in rechargeable lithium-ion battery last up to 5 hours of continuous use'}, {'feature': 'Compatible With
iOS:  iPad Air, iPad Air 2, iPad Mini 2 (w/ retina display), iPad Mini 3'}, {'feature': 'Also Compatible With
PC:  Windows 7, 8 or 10, Intel Core 2 Duo @ 2.0GHz or higher, 2GB RAM or higher'}]
longDescription: The first personal launch monitor of its kind, SkyTrak is a realistic and real-time golf practice and play system.  Keep your golf game sharp with a SkyTrak Launch Monitor and Golf Simulator.  This compact unit wirelessly connects to your compatible device and provides immediate shot launch data and ball flight visual feedback as soon as you hit the ball.  SkyTrak accurately measures ball speed, launch angle, backspin, club speed, sidespin and side angle and displays carry distance, offline and total distance to simulate practice and play as if you were on the course or practice tee.  Now integrated with Golf Course Simulation Partners like: World Golf Tour, TruGolf E6, and The Golf Club Game.  Each functionality allows users to play at some of the world’s top golf courses, all from the comfort of home.  Golf Course Simulation Partners require an additional fee on top of the SkyTrak Game Improvement Software Package.  Open up a new world of game improving practice and hours of entertaining away from the course.
name: SkyTrak - Golf Launch Monitor

longDescription: The skin inside the ear canal may become dry, irritated, or infected for a variety of reasons. People who spend a lot of time in the water, such as swimmers or divers, or those who over-clean their ears, may develop inflamed or irritated ear canal skin. Hearing aid users, patients with narrow ear canals, or those with a hereditary tendency to develop dry earwax may suffer from excessive or impacted wax buildup that is difficult to remove. Comfort Ear™ Natural Moisturizer promotes the normal flow of earwax and will not dry the ear canal skin like alcohol-based products. It moisturizes and protects the skin of the ear canal by lubricating and maintaining the proper pH balance.
name: Comfort Ear - ComfortEar X

longDescription: CarePenguin brings peace of mind to families with elderly or disabled loved ones living independently by detecting activity in a house through hot water use. features:
[{'feature': 'All Night Comfort, Year-Round
Made with naturally breathable down and a 100% cotton shell, our duvet keeps you comfortable in any season.'}, {'feature': 'Luxuriously Fluffy Down
Our sewn-in chamber design hugs your body like your favorite puffy jacket. The high-quality down stays in place all night long, so you can stay asleep.'}, {'feature': 'Ethically-Sourced
Our down is ethically-sourced and certified by the Responsible Down Stadnard (RDS), for all-natural comfort you can feel good about.'}]
longDescription: The Casper research and design team (the same one behind our award-winning mattress! ) created the Casper Down Duvet for your best nights rest. Designed for year-round use, the Casper Down Duvet uses naturally insulating duck down clusters to keep you comfortable and cozy. The carefully considered construction of the Down Duvet has proven to optimize your body’s natural temperature regulation — keeping you comfortable from dusk ’til dawn. The rectangular chambers drape perfectly across your body, while the seams prevent any fill from migrating. Combined with our highly breathable outer cotton shell, the Down Duvet insulates your body without trapping body heat. There are discreet tags on either end of the duvet to help identify the head and foot of the duvet — while loops in each corner ensure the duvet will stay in place within your cover. Easy to care for, machine wash cold on a gentle cycle with like colors. Tumble dry low.
name: Casper Down Duvet, Twin/Twin XL
